Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:10.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\c&H00FFFF&}字幕转制｜{\b1\c&HFFFFFF&}天外生物\N{\b0\c&H079FFF&}感谢原字幕制作者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.08,0:00:46.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我们是真正的行业\N{\rENG\i1}We were a real business.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.54,0:00:48.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}你要明白这一点\N{\rENG\i1}That's what you got to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.25,0:00:53.41,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我们这种行业\N{\rENG\i1}We were goddamn industry...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.84,0:00:57.67,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}是这个国家的支柱\N{\rENG\i1}the kind that's the backbone of this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.63,0:01:00.75,CHS,,0,0,0,,不用相信我的话\N{\rENG}Don't take my word for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.88,0:01:02.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,你亲自去停车场看看\N{\rENG}Go in the parking lot and look on the license
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.51,0:01:04.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,你那辆崭新的奔驰四五的牌照\N{\rENG}of that brand-new Mercedes 450 of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.06,0:01:08.55,CHS,,0,0,0,,喂 你看到了吗\N{\rENG}Hey. Are you seeing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.68,0:01:10.01,CHS,,0,0,0,,这位是弗尼斯・克里克\N{\rENG}That's Furnace Creek.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.14,0:01:11.68,CHS,,0,0,0,,这照片有一百年的历史了\N{\rENG}This, uh, picture's over 100 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.69,0:01:12.97,CHS,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\rENG}Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.10,0:01:14.97,CHS,,0,0,0,,看到这个英俊的人了吗\N{\rENG}And you see this handsome devil right here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.98,0:01:16.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\rENG}Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.73,0:01:18.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,他是我们威尔斯家的先人\N{\rENG}He's a Wells.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.36,0:01:22.15,CHS,,0,0,0,,好的 我知道你们是矿业公司\N{\rENG}Okay, so, um, I know you're a mining company,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.28,0:01:25.11,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 嗯  - 但我以为…\N{\rENG}- Mm-hmm.  - But I pictured...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.20,0:01:26.91,CHS,,0,0,0,,具体我也说不清楚\N{\rENG}Well, I don't know what I pictured exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.91,0:01:28.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,我以为会看到很多小矿车\N{\rENG}I guess little... little carts
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.75,0:01:30.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,在铁轨上跑\N{\rENG}going down little... little train tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.96,0:01:32.79,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 对  - 那你们在这儿是做什么的\N{\rENG}- Right.  - I mean, what is it that you do here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.87,0:01:34.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们做的是寻找金属\N{\rENG}Wh-what we do is we look for the metals
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.83,0:01:36.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,和矿石\N{\rENG}and the minerals, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.17,0:01:37.91,CHS,,0,0,0,,那是勘探部\N{\rENG}There's exploration over there,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.05,0:01:41.29,CHS,,0,0,0,,那是工程部和生产部\N{\rENG}there's engineering and there's production, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.42,0:01:43.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们是探矿者\N{\rENG}We're prospectors.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.89,0:01:46.55,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}还没懂？\N{\rENG\i1}Not yet'?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.64,0:01:48.05,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 我换个方式解释  - 好吧\N{\rENG}- Okay, how about this?  - Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.18,0:01:51.67,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们假设这个\N{\rENG}Um... so let's say that this...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.85,0:01:53.09,CHS,,0,0,0,,就是地球\N{\rENG}is the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.23,0:01:54.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,我的手提包？\N{\rENG}My handbag?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.27,0:01:55.93,CHS,,0,0,0,,你的手提包就是大地\N{\rENG}Your handbag is Mother Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.06,0:01:57.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,有着埋在深处的奥秘\N{\rENG}with all of her deep-filled mysteries
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.77,0:01:59.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,和好东西不愿被人拿走\N{\rENG}and goodies on the inside that she does not want to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.98,0:02:01.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,而我是人类\N{\rENG}Me, I'm man,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.82,0:02:03.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,对大地深处的东西很好奇\N{\rENG}and I'm damn curious about what she's got inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.03,0:02:07.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,于是我就进行钻探\N{\rENG}So, I send down what's called an exploratory drill.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.16,0:02:10.07,CHS,,0,0,0,,钻到里面找找看\N{\rENG}I go down inside and dig around,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.16,0:02:11.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,找到了什么\N{\rENG}come across something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.83,0:02:14.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,我取出来一看是镍\N{\rENG}I pull it out. It's nickel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.37,0:02:17.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,镍币其实是百分之七十五的铜和百分之二十五的镍\N{\rENG}Now, nickel's actually 75% copper and 25% nickel,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.88,0:02:19.21,CHS,,0,0,0,,反正世上有很多镍\N{\rENG}but there's a whole lot of nickel in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.21,0:02:21.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,世界需要镍\N{\rENG}and the world needs nickels.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.76,0:02:23.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,我又回去取出第二份样品\N{\rENG}I'm back down there getting my second core sample,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.97,0:02:26.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,碰巧发现了…\N{\rENG}and I happen to pull up, say...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.43,0:02:27.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,银\N{\rENG}silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.05,0:02:29.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,只要样品里有一点点银\N{\rENG}Now, the thing is, when you find a little bit of this,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.72,0:02:31.43,CHS,,0,0,0,,就意昧着可能有一个大银矿\N{\rENG}that means there could be a whole hell of a lot of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.43,0:02:32.97,CHS,,0,0,0,,然后我们开始筹集资金\N{\rENG}So we start raising money.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.10,0:02:35.47,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们筹集足够的钱来开矿\N{\rENG}We raise enough money to open a mine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.60,0:02:37.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,就像照片中的那个矿\N{\rENG}like the one in that picture right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.40,0:02:40.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,然后\N{\rENG}Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.73,0:02:42.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们都开采出来\N{\rENG}we dig it all up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.90,0:02:47.15,CHS,,0,0,0,,有时候 虽然不是经常 但有时候\N{\rENG}Now, sometimes... Not that often, but sometimes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.28,0:02:50.27,CHS,,0,0,0,,探矿之神们在天国之门开派对\N{\rENG}The prospecting gods are having a party at the Pearly Gates,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.45,0:02:53.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,而我们又非常幸运的话\N{\rENG}and we get real, real, really lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.50,0:02:55.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们在那里挖下去\N{\rENG}And we dig down in there,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.33,0:02:58.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,找到了一种金属 称作\N{\rENG}then we find a little metal called...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.33,0:03:00.33,CHS,,0,0,0,,金\N{\rENG}gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.34,0:03:06.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 是的  - 肯尼\N{\rENG}- Yes.  - Kenny.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.51,0:03:07.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,喜欢吗\N{\rENG}You like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.09,0:03:09.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,我爱你\N{\rENG}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.39,0:03:16.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,我爱你\N{\rENG}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.31,0:03:18.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,你爸找你\N{\rENG}Old man wants to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.69,0:03:21.35,CHS,,0,0,0,,下午好 玛丽安\N{\rENG}Afternoon, Marianne.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.48,0:03:23.35,CHS,,0,0,0,,爸 你找我？\N{\rENG}Hey, Pop. Heard you want to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.36,0:03:24.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,是的 肯尼\N{\rENG}Yeah, Kenny.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.74,0:03:27.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,你过来一下\N{\rENG}Get your ass in here, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.24,0:03:28.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,你在跟找讲讲\N{\rENG}Would you, uh, run through this
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.74,0:03:30.61,CHS,,0,0,0,,潘兴县的这个开发计划\N{\rENG}Pershing County strategy again for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.74,0:03:32.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,好\N{\rENG}Right, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.99,0:03:35.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,是关于南部纽蒙特公司的一个矿区\N{\rENG}It's about this southern part of this Newmont property,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.50,0:03:36.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,在这里\N{\rENG}right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.87,0:03:39.21,CHS,,0,0,0,,纽蒙特公司只钻了一百四十米深\N{\rENG}Now, Newmont just started drilling 140 meters
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.38,0:03:41.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,就发现了大量的菱镁矿\N{\rENG}and they're finding a whole lot of magnesite.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.13,0:03:43.87,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果你记得 我们依然有瑞利夫峡谷的优先选择权\N{\rENG}If you remember, we still own the option on Relief Canyon,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.01,0:03:46.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,跟他们紧邻 却什么也没找到 为什么呢\N{\rENG}which is next door. We're not finding squat, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.22,0:03:47.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,因为钻的不够深\N{\rENG}We're not drilling deep enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.88,0:03:49.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,让我们回到那里 钻得更深\N{\rENG}Let's get back in there. Drill deeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.72,0:03:52.71,CHS,,0,0,0,,必要的话就钻一百四十米 就能很有机会\N{\rENG}Go to 140 if we need to, and we got a damn good chance
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.85,0:03:54.68,CHS,,0,0,0,,在瑞利夫峡谷进行开发\N{\rENG}of getting Relief back in production.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.81,0:03:56.67,CHS,,0,0,0,,杰利特峡谷呢\N{\rENG}What about Jerritt Canyon?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.81,0:03:58.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,那是你的宝贝\N{\rENG}Well, that's your baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.81,0:04:01.05,CHS,,0,0,0,,你对它的了解比我多得多\N{\rENG}You know a hell of a lot more about it than I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.19,0:04:02.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,但化验结果很乐观\N{\rENG}But the assays look promising.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.90,0:04:04.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,可能是个大矿\N{\rENG}Could be fucking huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.49,0:04:11.35,CHS,,0,0,0,,我要你亲自负责这事\N{\rENG}I want you to run point on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.53,0:04:13.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,全盘负责\N{\rENG}All in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.83,0:04:15.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,把它做大\N{\rENG}Scale it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.00,0:04:17.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,成为你的业绩\N{\rENG}Make it yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.96,0:04:20.45,CHS,,0,0,0,,是\N{\rENG}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.00,0:04:25.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,克莱夫・科尔曼也赞成\N{\rENG}Clive Coleman's on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.21,0:04:26.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,他们和你一起去\N{\rENG}Those boys will ride with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.22,0:04:36.43,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们在这一行业辛苦努力\N{\rENG}God, we work hard in this business.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.56,0:04:38.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,时常一无所获\N{\rENG}Sometimes for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.35,0:04:42.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,我每天早上醒来 对自己说\N{\rENG}I wake up every morning. I tell myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.69,0:04:45.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,干这一行不是苦差事\N{\rENG}"I don't have to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.53,0:04:47.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,而是我的幸运\N{\rENG}I get to do this."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.86,0:04:53.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,然后就只是蓝天\N{\rENG}And then it's just blue skies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.29,0:05:05.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,蓝天啊\N{\rENG}Blue skies, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.92,0:05:11.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我的父亲\N{\rENG\i1}My old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.38,0:05:13.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,是个传奇\N{\rENG}a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.76,0:05:18.25,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}这是我最后一次见到他\N{\rENG\i1}That was the last time I saw him alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.67,0:05:53.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,来杯醒眼酒吗 肯尼\N{\rENG}A little eye-opener, Kenny?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.38,0:05:55.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,上帝保佑你 罗伊\N{\rENG}God bless you, Roy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.72,0:05:58.63,CHS,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\rENG}Here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.77,0:06:01.13,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 为主矿脉干杯  - 主矿脉\N{\rENG}- Boys, to the mother lode.  - Mother lode.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.27,0:06:03.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,就在今天\N{\rENG}Today be the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.35,0:06:05.31,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}这一地区的地质学报告\N{\rENG\i1}The geological reports on this
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.44,0:06:06.47,CHS,,0,0,0,,非常的乐观\N{\rENG}are highly encouraging.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.61,0:06:09.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们将开始大规模勘探\N{\rENG}We are taking a very aggressive approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.19,0:06:10.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,招股书？当然\N{\rENG}Prospectus? Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.28,0:06:12.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,我可以让秘书马上发给你一份\N{\rENG}I can have my secretary send you one right out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.07,0:06:14.23,CHS,,0,0,0,,但我要告诉你 这一项目\N{\rENG}But I got to tell you, this offering,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.36,0:06:16.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,己经有太多人认购了\N{\rENG}it's already over-subscribed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.16,0:06:18.11,CHS,,0,0,0,,但下个项目可以给你留一些\N{\rENG}You know, we can always try and get you in on the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.12,0:06:20.73,CHS,,0,0,0,,没事 我理解\N{\rENG}No, no. Yea, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.87,0:06:23.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,该死的\N{\rENG}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.21,0:06:25.95,CHS,,0,0,0,,你看时间 己经十一点一刻了 肯尼\N{\rENG}Watching the time? It's 11:15, Kenny.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.08,0:06:28.45,CHS,,0,0,0,,老天\N{\rENG}Oh, Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.38,0:06:32.25,CHS,,0,0,0,,没有你我可怎么办\N{\rENG}Where would I be without you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.56,0:06:41.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,威尔斯先生\N{\rENG}Mr. Wells?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.72,0:06:43.43,CHS,,0,0,0,,是我 我是劳埃德・斯坦顿\N{\rENG}Yes. Lloyd Stanton.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.56,0:06:45.27,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 你好 劳埃德  - 嗨\N{\rENG}- Hello, Lloyd. Kenny Wells.  - Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.35,0:06:46.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,这是我的同事亨利・安德鲁斯\N{\rENG}This is my colleague, Henry Andrews.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.85,0:06:48.01,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 很高兴见到你  - 嗨\N{\rENG}- Pleased to meet you.  - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.02,0:06:50.23,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 到后面谈吧  - 好\N{\rENG}- Come on back.  - Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.36,0:06:52.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rENG}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.03,0:06:58.99,CHS,,0,0,0,,找我们有什么事\N{\rENG}So, what can we do for ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.08,0:07:00.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们等克莱夫来了再谈吧\N{\rENG}Well, why don't we wait for Clive?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.08,0:07:03.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,他正开会 分不开身\N{\rENG}Oh, uh, Mr. Coleman got tied up in a meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.50,0:07:04.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,两位别介意\N{\rENG}No offense, boys,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.96,0:07:07.07,CHS,,0,0,0,,我本来是来见克莱夫的\N{\rENG}but I'm supposed to be meeting with Clive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.21,0:07:08.99,CHS,,0,0,0,,不介意 但如果你够资格\N{\rENG}None taken, but if you were supposed to be
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.13,0:07:11.21,CHS,,0,0,0,,就肯定能见到克莱夫\N{\rENG}meeting with Clive, you would be meeting with Clive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.26,0:07:16.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,好吧情况是这样的\N{\rENG}All right. Here is what we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.26,0:07:19.25,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们正在开发一些地方\N{\rENG}We are developing some very exciting properties
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.39,0:07:22.13,CHS,,0,0,0,,正符合你们的投资者的需要\N{\rENG}that are spot-on for your investor profile.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.27,0:07:26.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,低价买 进升值潜力巨大\N{\rENG}Low buy-in with a sizable upside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.10,0:07:28.51,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 嗯嗯  - 而且更好的是\N{\rENG}- Mm-hmm.  - And the beautiful part is
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.52,0:07:32.23,CHS,,0,0,0,,只有十二到十八月的资金回笼时间\N{\rENG}they are all only 12 to 18 months and cash positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.36,0:07:33.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 马尼托巴湖？ - 是的\N{\rENG}- Manitoba?  - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.73,0:07:36.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们在一个拍卖会上得到的选择权\N{\rENG}We picked up an option on a skip claim at an auction.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.65,0:07:38.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,对 可这是九十天的选择\N{\rENG}Right, but it's a 90-day option.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.28,0:07:39.61,CHS,,0,0,0,,是的窗口期很短\N{\rENG}Yes, the window is narrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.74,0:07:41.11,CHS,,0,0,0,,但如果你们看看地质报告\N{\rENG}but if you have a look at the Jerritt,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.12,0:07:42.53,CHS,,0,0,0,,会看到很有潜力的页岩结构\N{\rENG}you'll see a very promising shale formation
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.54,0:07:44.87,CHS,,0,0,0,,还被开发过\N{\rENG}that hasn't been tapped yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.67,0:07:49.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,威尔斯先生 瓦肖公司的市值\N{\rENG}Mr. Wells, Washoe has a practical value
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.92,0:07:51.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,只比O高一点点\N{\rENG}hovering just above zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.29,0:07:53.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,你们负债累累\N{\rENG}Your debt load is untenable,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.21,0:07:55.95,CHS,,0,0,0,,而你带来的只是一片原始土地 既没有基础设施\N{\rENG}and you bring us, uh, raw land with no infrastructure,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.13,0:07:58.37,CHS,,0,0,0,,也没有可互换资产 这实在…\N{\rENG}no fungible assets. I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.51,0:08:00.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们不可能会认购的\N{\rENG}you can't possibly expect us to underwrite this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.22,0:08:02.43,CHS,,0,0,0,,这可是价格极低\N{\rENG}Yeah. I'm talking about a small offering here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.56,0:08:04.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,就像我一开始说的 低价买进\N{\rENG}As I said in the beginning, a low buy-in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.22,0:08:06.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果你们再看看地质报告\N{\rENG}Now, if you'll take a second look at the Jerritt,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.48,0:08:08.51,CHS,,0,0,0,,就能看到我所看到的\N{\rENG}you will see what I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.64,0:08:11.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,就是利润\N{\rENG}And that's money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.19,0:08:15.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,但不是我们的利润\N{\rENG}Not our money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.30,0:08:43.79,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}现实是\N{\rENG\i1}See, the... the thing is
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.97,0:08:46.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}整体经济不景气\N{\rENG\i1}that the whole economy had turned,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.31,0:08:48.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}尤其是商品经济\N{\rENG\i1}particularly for commodities.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.27,0:08:52.93,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}当天收盘时\N{\rENG\i1}Close of the day,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.06,0:08:55.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}瓦肖公司的股价是每股四美分\N{\rENG\i1}Washoe was trading at four cents a share
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.53,0:08:57.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}依然无人问津\N{\rENG\i1}if it was trading at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.82,0:08:59.93,CHS,,0,0,0,,瓦肖矿业公司有个很棒的土地租赁\N{\rENG}Washoe Mining. There's this great little land lease.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.07,0:09:03.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,这是个千载难逢的机会\N{\rENG}'Cause this is a once in a lifetime opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.57,0:09:05.41,CHS,,0,0,0,,对 瓦肖 瓦肖矿业公司\N{\rENG}Right. Washoe. Washoe Mining.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.58,0:09:07.99,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们还在营业\N{\rENG}You know, carrying the... carrying on the business.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.12,0:09:10.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,矿物是肯定有的\N{\rENG}You know, there's still minerals out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.71,0:09:11.95,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们只需要找到\N{\rENG}We just got to find them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.96,0:09:13.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,好 好的\N{\rENG}Yeah, all right, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.04,0:09:14.53,CHS,,0,0,0,,谢谢你抽出时间 再见\N{\rENG}Thank... thank you for your time. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.42,0:09:18.63,CHS,,0,0,0,,我可以…\N{\rENG}I could...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.71,0:09:20.25,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}十二到十八个月…\N{\rENG\i1}12 to 18 months...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.38,0:09:22.29,CHS,,0,0,0,,现金净流入\N{\rENG}cash positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.43,0:09:24.79,CHS,,0,0,0,,一笔交易…\N{\rENG}A deal...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.93,0:09:26.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,我就给你打电话\N{\rENG}Goddamn, I am calling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.18,0:09:27.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,不管现在是几点了\N{\rENG}Fuck whatever time it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.81,0:09:32.68,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}瓦肖矿业\N{\rENG\i1}Washoe Mining,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.85,0:09:34.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}这公司是我祖父\N{\rENG\i1}the company that my grandfather
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.77,0:09:37.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}在内华达山区白手起家\N{\rENG\i1}literally scratched out of the side of a Nevada mountain,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.11,0:09:42.15,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我父亲又一手把公司做大\N{\rENG\i1}the company that my father made into a real player,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.28,0:09:45.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}到我手上却垮了\N{\rENG\i1}was almost gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.45,0:09:47.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}几乎垮了\N{\rENG\i1}Almost.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.87,0:09:55.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我己经失去了我的房子\N{\rENG\i1}I'd already, uh, lost my house,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.33,0:09:58.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我是住在凯的房子里\N{\rENG\i1}and I was, uh... I was living with Kay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.55,0:10:02.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}那个房子也快保不住了\N{\rENG\i1}And, uh, we-we were about to lose that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.73,0:10:15.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我喝半加仑的施格兰金酒\N{\rENG\i1}I had a half gallon of Seagram's in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.86,0:10:18.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}换成别人早就喝死了 但我不会\N{\rENG\i1}Shit, most people would have been dead, but not me. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.44,0:10:22.31,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}相反\N{\rENG\i1}Instead...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.45,0:10:24.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我有一个梦\N{\rENG\i1}I had a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.49,0:10:31.45,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}是真的做了…\N{\rENG\i1}I mean, I mean, I mean, literally, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.58,0:10:34.41,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}做了个梦\N{\rENG\i1}I had a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.76,0:10:44.21,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}印尼\N{\rENG\i1}Indonesia.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.34,0:10:46.13,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}金子\N{\rENG\i1}Gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.01,0:10:52.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我五六年前去过印尼\N{\rENG\i1}Now, I'd been to Indonesia five or six years earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.73,0:10:54.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}那时我还有点钱\N{\rENG\i1}I still had a little money in my pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.69,0:10:56.35,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}印尼也在快速发展\N{\rENG\i1}You know, Indonesia was booming,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.44,0:10:58.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我去寻找投资的机会\N{\rENG\i1}and I was looking for a way to get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.19,0:11:04.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}在那时 如果你想\N{\rENG\i1}Back then, if you wanted
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.03,0:11:06.61,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}在印尼寻找矿产\N{\rENG\i1}to put a hole in the ground in Indonesia,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.61,0:11:09.73,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}就需要迈克・阿克斯塔告诉你应该在哪儿挖\N{\rENG\i1}you wanted Mike Acosta telling you where to dig.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.87,0:11:12.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}他就是他们所谓的河行者\N{\rENG\i1}He's what they called a River Walker.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.33,0:11:13.99,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}真正的地质学者\N{\rENG\i1}Yeah, a real hands-on geologist.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.12,0:11:15.11,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}有真本事\N{\rENG\i1}The real deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.04,0:11:18.33,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}上过牛津大学 麻省理工\N{\rENG\i1}Oxford College, MIT.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.46,0:11:19.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}母亲是委内瑞拉人\N{\rENG\i1}His mom was Venezuelan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.84,0:11:22.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}父亲是英国人\N{\rENG\i1}His dad was English.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.17,0:11:25.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}现在你看，他刚刚发现了…\N{\rENG\i1}Now, you see, he'd just discovered
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.56,0:11:28.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}东南亚最大的铜矿\N{\rENG\i1}the largest copper strike in Southeast Asia,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.30,0:11:32.51,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}人人都想得到他 包括我\N{\rENG\i1}and everybody wanted a piece of him, including me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.64,0:11:35.35,CHS,,0,0,0,,纳斯卡板块 太平洋板块\N{\rENG}You got the Nazca Plate, the Pacific Plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.43,0:11:37.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,胡安・德富卡 北美 南美\N{\rENG}Juan de Fuca, North American, South American.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.90,0:11:39.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿留申 马里亚纳 汤家\N{\rENG}Aleutian, Marianas, Tonga.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.77,0:11:42.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,这些板块之问互相摩擦\N{\rENG}The plates rubbing and grinding up on each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.61,0:11:44.27,CHS,,0,0,0,,六万亿公斤的压力\N{\rENG}Six trillion kilobytes of pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.40,0:11:48.15,CHS,,0,0,0,,一万摄氏度在环太平洋地带\N{\rENG}10,000 degrees Celsius kicking up geothermic hot spots
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.28,0:11:50.15,CHS,,0,0,0,,形成了地热圈\N{\rENG}all along the Pacific rim.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.28,0:11:54.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}他称之为火山地震带理论\N{\rENG\i1}He called it the, uh, the Ring of Fire theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.54,0:11:56.53,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}吸引了每个人\N{\rENG\i1}And he definitely had everyone's attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.66,0:11:59.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,我就是这么找到铜矿的\N{\rENG}That's how I found the copper.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.33,0:12:02.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,所以我也会找到金矿\N{\rENG}And that's why I'll find the gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.52,0:12:19.01,CHS,,0,0,0,,你这么早起了\N{\rENG}You're up early.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.15,0:12:20.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,嗨\N{\rENG}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.02,0:12:24.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,你昨天想说什么来着\N{\rENG}You want to talk about yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.73,0:12:27.85,CHS,,0,0,0,,不 我得走了 我有个计划\N{\rENG}No. I gotta go right now, babe. I've gotta plan. Gotta plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.99,0:12:30.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 等等 肯尼 听着  - 嗯？\N{\rENG}- Oh, wait, Kenny, Kenny, listen.  - Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.32,0:12:32.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,卡尔有个工作\N{\rENG}Carl had an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.32,0:12:34.61,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 美国之家的卡尔？ - 嗯\N{\rENG}- American Home Carl?  - Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.74,0:12:37.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,他说如果你愿意 你可以在那里\N{\rENG}He said he could, uh, get you on for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.46,0:12:39.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 先干一段时间  - 好 好\N{\rENG}- if you wanted.  - Right, right, right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.17,0:12:41.91,CHS,,0,0,0,,我觉得没这个必要 亲爱的\N{\rENG}Yeah, I don't think that's going to be necessary, babe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.04,0:12:43.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,只是暂时的\N{\rENG}Yeah, but it'd just be temporary
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.79,0:12:45.41,CHS,,0,0,0,,等到经济好转\N{\rENG}till the market turns.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.55,0:12:48.63,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们还可以在仓库里胡来\N{\rENG}We could fool around in the warehouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.76,0:12:50.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,我告诉你\N{\rENG}You know, I tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.59,0:12:53.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,我先出一趟差\N{\rENG}When I get done with this trip, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.26,0:12:54.55,CHS,,0,0,0,,不会超过一周\N{\rENG}Shouldn't take more than a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.56,0:12:56.01,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 好吧  - 什么 你要去哪儿\N{\rENG}- All right.  - What? Where you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.10,0:12:58.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 如果不成功 再联系卡尔也不迟  - 宝贝…\N{\rENG}- If it doesn't work out, I'll give Carl a call.  - Baby...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.52,0:13:00.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 我去了机场会给你打电话  - 等等\N{\rENG}- I'll call you from the airport.  - Wait. Wait, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.27,0:13:01.55,CHS,,0,0,0,,肯尼\N{\rENG}Kenny!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.69,0:13:05.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}就像我得到了召唤一样\N{\rENG\i1}It was like I was being called, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.86,0:13:09.23,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}金子的召唤\N{\rENG\i1}It was the gold calling.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.36,0:13:11.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}你可能觉得这很疯狂\N{\rENG\i1}That may sound crazy to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.24,0:13:13.15,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}但如果你体会过这种感觉\N{\rENG\i1}but if you... if you knew that feeling,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.28,0:13:15.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,你就能理解\N{\rENG}well, you'd know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.32,0:13:51.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我是肯尼・威尔斯 我就在\N{\rENG\i1}Kenny Wells. I'm down here in the, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.32,0:13:52.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,雅加达皇宫酒店的大堂里\N{\rENG}the lobby of the, uh, Jakarta Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.86,0:13:54.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,听着\N{\rENG}Uh... Yeah, listen,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.62,0:13:56.11,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我们肯定抱时间搞混了\N{\rENG\i1}we must've got the times mixed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.20,0:13:58.11,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}让我知道 我在这里\N{\rENG\i1}Um... Let me know. I'm down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.24,0:14:01.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我穿着西装 坐在绿色沙发上\N{\rENG\i1}I'm in the brown suit, I'm on the green couch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.50,0:14:02.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,是个帅小伙\N{\rENG}I'm the good-looking guy, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.79,0:14:04.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,好 我们会成功的\N{\rENG}All right. We'll make it happen, Fuca.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.29,0:14:05.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,好\N{\rENG}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.38,0:14:11.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,威尔斯？\N{\rENG}Wells?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.72,0:14:13.55,CHS,,0,0,0,,迈克\N{\rENG}Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.47,0:14:18.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,很高兴再次见到你\N{\rENG}Good to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.06,0:14:22.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,我知道一个地方卖酒的\N{\rENG}I know a local place, a bit more color.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.35,0:14:24.47,CHS,,0,0,0,,这里不卖酒吗\N{\rENG}What, they're not pouring here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.81,0:14:27.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\rENG}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.94,0:14:30.81,CHS,,0,0,0,,那么\N{\rENG}So,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.94,0:14:33.53,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们在这里谈什么 威尔斯？\N{\rENG}what are we talking about here, Wells?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.45,0:14:37.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,火山地震带 迈克\N{\rENG}Ring of Fire, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.12,0:14:38.61,CHS,,0,0,0,,火山地震带理论\N{\rENG}Ring of Fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.74,0:14:41.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,你在谈我最大的发现\N{\rENG}You're playing my greatest hits.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.83,0:14:44.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,那个火己经灭了\N{\rENG}Fire's gone out of that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.16,0:14:45.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,何出此言\N{\rENG}Well, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.04,0:14:49.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,这是一个很有声望的地质学家的观点\N{\rENG}It's the opinion of my fellow esteemed geologists,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.00,0:14:52.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,我的火山地震带理论用他的话来说\N{\rENG}that the whole thing... I'm quoting here...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.59,0:14:54.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,就是一佗屎\N{\rENG}Is a crock of shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.72,0:14:56.75,CHS,,0,0,0,,那也没办法\N{\rENG}Well, what the hell, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.89,0:14:58.63,CHS,,0,0,0,,你搞错了\N{\rENG}You called it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.85,0:15:01.71,CHS,,0,0,0,,你打算怎么办\N{\rENG}What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.85,0:15:04.51,CHS,,0,0,0,,在这一行 没什么对错\N{\rENG}There's no right or wrong in this business.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.64,0:15:06.93,CHS,,0,0,0,,只有找到和找不到\N{\rENG}There's only hits and misses.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.06,0:15:09.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,这里有金子\N{\rENG}There's gold here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.78,0:15:18.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,很高兴你这么说 迈克\N{\rENG}I'm glad you said that, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.53,0:15:20.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,我是真心高兴 因为我\N{\rENG}I truly am, 'cause I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.45,0:15:24.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,相信你\N{\rENG}believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.12,0:15:26.41,CHS,,0,0,0,,我不想给你泼玲水 但你以为\N{\rENG}I hate to dash your hopes, but don't you think
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.54,0:15:28.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,没有别人抱着同样的想法来找过我吗\N{\rENG}others have come along before you with the same thought
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.63,0:15:32.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,而且从衣着看 比你更有钱的人\N{\rENG}and, from the looks of it, deeper pockets?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.63,0:15:35.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,火山地震带是真实存在的 迈克\N{\rENG}Ring of Fire is real, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.47,0:15:36.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,我第一次听说时就相信\N{\rENG}I knew it the first time I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.93,0:15:38.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,我就像受到电击一般\N{\rENG}It struck me like a fucking lightning bolt,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.72,0:15:40.33,CHS,,0,0,0,,从没忘记当时的感觉\N{\rENG}and I never forgot it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.47,0:15:42.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,你就笑我吧 经常有人嘲笑我\N{\rENG}Go ahead, laugh. I get that all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.60,0:15:45.09,CHS,,0,0,0,,但你听着\N{\rENG}But hear this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.23,0:15:47.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,我不只是相信\N{\rENG}I don't just believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.52,0:15:48.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,我是确定\N{\rENG}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.10,0:15:51.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 不会  - 我亲眼见过\N{\rENG}- No, you don't.  - I've seen it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.27,0:15:54.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,你不懂\N{\rENG}You don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.53,0:15:57.73,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 没人会资助我  - 我会\N{\rENG}- No one will back me.  - I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.86,0:15:59.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,你只要告诉我应该在哪儿钻探\N{\rENG}You tell me where you want to dig, Mikey,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.07,0:16:02.99,CHS,,0,0,0,,费用我全包\N{\rENG}and I'll make goddamn sure the bills are paid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.24,0:16:05.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,恕我直言威尔斯\N{\rENG}No offense, Wells, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.96,0:16:08.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,但看你衣着 恐怕机票钱也是靠打劫凑的\N{\rENG}you look like you had to rob someone just to get here, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.79,0:16:11.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,你对我一无所知\N{\rENG}You know nothing about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.75,0:16:13.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,你确信这里有金子\N{\rENG}You know it's still out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.21,0:16:17.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,这是肯定的\N{\rENG}I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.42,0:16:20.29,CHS,,0,0,0,,从你的眼神能看出来 你仍然相信\N{\rENG}I can see it in your eyes. You still believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.18,0:16:25.47,CHS,,0,0,0,,我能理解 我也是生在山脚下\N{\rENG}I get it, and I was born on the side of the mountain, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.60,0:16:27.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,我父亲的一切财产\N{\rENG}My-my father scratched everything he ever owned
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.27,0:16:28.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,都是他从矿石里一点点挖出来的\N{\rENG}out of a fucking rock. All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.73,0:16:30.01,CHS,,0,0,0,,去世时指甲里依然有泥土\N{\rENG}Died with dirt under his fingernails,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.02,0:16:31.68,CHS,,0,0,0,,我也想像他那样\N{\rENG}and I intend to do the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.86,0:16:33.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,这一行业\N{\rENG}This business...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.73,0:16:35.31,CHS,,0,0,0,,几年前就把我淘汰了\N{\rENG}wrote me off years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.44,0:16:36.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,而你现在也不是\N{\rENG}All right, maybe you're not running the hottest
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.78,0:16:38.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,在事业巅峰\N{\rENG}in your career right now either,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.03,0:16:39.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,让我们证明他们错了\N{\rENG}so let's prove them wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.32,0:16:40.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,你和我\N{\rENG}You and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.66,0:16:41.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,让我们证明他们都错了\N{\rENG}Let's prove them all fucking wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.91,0:16:43.15,CHS,,0,0,0,,知道为什么吗\N{\rENG}And you know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.37,0:16:46.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,你知道为什么 因为火山地震带理论\N{\rENG}You do know why, because the Ring of Fire
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.83,0:16:49.95,CHS,,0,0,0,,是正确的 迈克 你是对的\N{\rENG}is right, Mike. You called it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.08,0:16:52.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,只是还没有找到它\N{\rENG}You just haven't found it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.84,0:16:57.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果你说我疯了\N{\rENG}Tell me I'm crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.21,0:16:59.55,CHS,,0,0,0,,我马上坐飞机回去\N{\rENG}I'll be on the next plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.47,0:17:06.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,你疯了\N{\rENG}You're crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.32,0:17:17.81,CHS,,0,0,0,,你有帽子吗 威尔斯？\N{\rENG}You have a hat, Wells?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.99,0:17:23.35,CHS,,0,0,0,,是的 我有帽子\N{\rENG}Yeah, I got a hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.53,0:17:24.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们要去哪儿吗\N{\rENG}Why, we going somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.03,0:17:27.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}上游\N{\rENG\i1}Up river.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.83,0:17:30.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}是什么河 迈克\N{\rENG\i1}What river is that, Mike?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.37,0:17:32.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,你迟到了\N{\rENG}You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.12,0:17:33.91,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}唯一重要的一条河\N{\rENG\i1}The only one that matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.03,0:18:00.89,CHS,,0,0,0,,蒂亚克人在这条河上淘金\N{\rENG}The Dayak have been panning this river
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.03,0:18:03.49,CHS,,0,0,0,,有五千多年的历史了\N{\rENG}for over 5,000 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.66,0:18:06.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,这就是河名的由来\N{\rENG}That's how it got its name,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.16,0:18:08.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,Daya Kensana！\N{\rENG}Daya Kensana.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.33,0:18:09.91,CHS,,0,0,0,,是什么意思\N{\rENG}What's it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.04,0:18:11.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,Daya意思是上游\N{\rENG}"Daya" means "upstream."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.79,0:18:14.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,Kensana意思是金子\N{\rENG}"Kensana" means "gold."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.88,0:18:18.29,CHS,,0,0,0,,你就靠一河名？\N{\rENG}You got to be shitting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.44,0:18:41.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,威尔斯\N{\rENG}Wells. Wells.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.36,0:18:42.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们到了\N{\rENG}We're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.07,0:18:46.23,CHS,,0,0,0,,听着 蒂亚克人是好斗的民族\N{\rENG}So, listen, the Dayak are warrior people,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.37,0:18:48.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,最著名的是蒂亚克\N{\rENG}probably best known for Dayak,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.99,0:18:50.61,CHS,,0,0,0,,即猎取人头\N{\rENG}headhunting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.74,0:18:53.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,但现在不常有了\N{\rENG}But it doesn't happen much anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.29,0:18:55.15,CHS,,0,0,0,,他们会以为我们是什么商人\N{\rENG}They might be thinking we're some traders
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.33,0:18:56.45,CHS,,0,0,0,,或者是某人的岳母\N{\rENG}or someone's mother-in-law.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.73,0:19:17.81,CHS,,0,0,0,,还有多远\N{\rENG}How long?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.11,0:19:21.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,这片丛林会考验你\N{\rENG}This jungle will... will test you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.82,0:19:26.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,会把你抱起来 搪量你一下\N{\rENG}It will hold you up, weigh you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.99,0:19:28.73,CHS,,0,0,0,,判断你值多少盎司\N{\rENG}and decide your worth within an ounce.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.87,0:19:30.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,你总是这么说话吗\N{\rENG}Do you always talk like this, Mike?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.70,0:19:33.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,就像录音机一样\N{\rENG}Like a book on tape?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.33,0:19:35.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,可能吧\N{\rENG}I suppose I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.79,0:19:40.53,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们去哪？\N{\rENG}Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.67,0:19:42.33,CHS,,0,0,0,,向上\N{\rENG}Up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.10,0:19:57.31,CHS,,0,0,0,,你看\N{\rENG}Take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.74,0:20:08.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,我的天啊\N{\rENG}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.91,0:20:14.87,CHS,,0,0,0,,这就是我梦里看到的\N{\rENG}It's my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.00,0:20:16.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,多年来一直有人\N{\rENG}There have been a few folks up here
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.00,0:20:18.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,在这里勘探\N{\rENG}tapping over the years,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.92,0:20:21.75,CHS,,0,0,0,,但他们只专注于南部的山麓\N{\rENG}but have all focused on the foothills far to the south.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.88,0:20:25.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,但让我感兴趣的是另一个方向\N{\rENG}But what interests me is the other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.38,0:20:27.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,那个小凹陷\N{\rENG}That small depression,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.55,0:20:31.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,就像一个巨人留下的脚印一样\N{\rENG}like a giant left a footprint walking away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.39,0:20:33.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,那里肯定发生了什么 威尔斯\N{\rENG}Something happened there, Wells.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.06,0:20:37.89,CHS,,0,0,0,,非同寻常的事\N{\rENG}Something hot and angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.02,0:20:40.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们就去那里寻找宝藏\N{\rENG}That's where we'll find the tasty bits.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.98,0:20:43.47,CHS,,0,0,0,,我的梦境\N{\rENG}My dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.32,0:20:50.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,金子就在那里\N{\rENG}is out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.41,0:20:52.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,这是肯定的\N{\rENG}Damn right it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.54,0:20:57.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}如果你考虑的\N{\rENG\i1}Look, if it's the big boys
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.70,0:20:59.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}投资我们的是些大户\N{\rENG\i1}that you're thinking about investing in us...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.54,0:21:01.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}比如哈佛基金\N{\rENG\i1}You know, the Harvard endowment
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.29,0:21:03.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}或者某个退休基金\N{\rENG\i1}or some... some pension fund, right?...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.84,0:21:06.33,CHS,,0,0,0,,那你不该找我\N{\rENG}I am not your guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.46,0:21:08.95,CHS,,0,0,0,,但那些散户\N{\rENG}But the little guys, right,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.13,0:21:10.71,CHS,,0,0,0,,你根没听说过的那些人\N{\rENG}guys that you don't even know about,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.84,0:21:12.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,皮条客小混混\N{\rENG}the, uh, the hustlers, the scrappers,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.64,0:21:14.47,CHS,,0,0,0,,那些能把事情办成的人\N{\rENG}the make-it-happen motherfuckers,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.55,0:21:16.47,CHS,,0,0,0,,就是我要找的人\N{\rENG}those are my guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.85,0:21:20.51,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们需要多少钱\N{\rENG}How much do we need?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.60,0:21:24.31,CHS,,0,0,0,,启动资金要七十到七十五万美元\N{\rENG}Seven. Seven-fifty to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.44,0:21:26.85,CHS,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\rENG}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.82,0:21:30.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,但我们需要多少钱？\N{\rENG}How much do we need?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.49,0:21:32.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,不只是租块地这么简单\N{\rENG}It isn't just a lease.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.70,0:21:34.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们是在印尼\N{\rENG}We're in Indonesia.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.53,0:21:38.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,这意昧着要拿到许可证贿赔官员\N{\rENG}That means getting a permit and lining pockets.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.83,0:21:40.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,需要设备搞挖掘\N{\rENG}Equipment. You don't just do this
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.75,0:21:42.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,不可能只靠铁镐\N{\rENG}with a couple of shovels and a pickax.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.37,0:21:43.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,我会搞到钱的\N{\rENG}I'll get the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.04,0:21:45.75,CHS,,0,0,0,,不管需要多少\N{\rENG}Whatever it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.89,0:21:58.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 这是什么  - 这是合同\N{\rENG}- What's that?  - It's a contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.39,0:21:59.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,你看看\N{\rENG}Read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.02,0:22:01.97,CHS,,0,0,0,,然后签字\N{\rENG}Sign it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.99,0:22:18.95,CHS,,0,0,0,,留着吧\N{\rENG}Keep it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.58,0:22:23.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我有强烈的直觉\N{\rENG\i1}I could feel it in my bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.37,0:22:26.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我推销的是我真心相信的东西\N{\rENG\i1}I was selling something that I believed in.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.38,0:22:30.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,最低认购两万股\N{\rENG}20-K minimum buy-in, right,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.76,0:22:32.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,股票正被迅速抢购中\N{\rENG}and the shares are fucking flying off the shelf.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.63,0:22:33.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,有风险才有利润\N{\rENG}I mean, no risk, no gain, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.97,0:22:36.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,现在就在发生\N{\rENG}No, 'cause it's coming in right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.55,0:22:38.29,CHS,,0,0,0,,不 阿科斯塔 迈克・阿科斯塔\N{\rENG}No, Acosta. Michael Acosta.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.43,0:22:39.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,他发现了史上最大的铜矿\N{\rENG}It's the largest copper strike in history,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.64,0:22:41.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,他就是我们的专家\N{\rENG}and that's the guy that we got.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.22,0:22:43.01,CHS,,0,0,0,,凯 把鞋子擦亮 准备跳舞\N{\rENG}Kay, get those shoes shined for dancing, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.02,0:22:44.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我们连勘探许可证都还没拿到\N{\rENG\i1}We don't even have the exploration permits.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.27,0:22:46.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们的卖点是什么\N{\rENG}What are they selling?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.77,0:22:48.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们的卖点？\N{\rENG}What are we selling?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.19,0:22:52.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们的卖点就是个故事\N{\rENG}Mikey, we're selling the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.11,0:22:54.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,而这个故事就是你\N{\rENG}And right now, the story is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.03,0:22:57.27,CHS,,0,0,0,,说到你 你现在干什么呢\N{\rENG}Speaking of which, what the fuck are you doing right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.37,0:22:59.95,CHS,,0,0,0,,我正在古邦市看一套钻探设备\N{\rENG}I'm down in Kupang City looking at coring equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.04,0:23:02.95,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿科斯塔正在古邦市看一套钻探设备\N{\rENG}Acosta's in Kupang City looking at coring equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.04,0:23:04.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,他现在就在古邦市\N{\rENG}He's in Kupang City as we speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.75,0:23:06.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,那是个…\N{\rENG}It-it's a fucking...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.71,0:23:08.45,CHS,,0,0,0,,古邦市 我们正在购买钻探设备\N{\rENG}Kupang City. We're getting the coring equipment...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.46,0:23:10.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,你是传奇 迈克 你就是传奇\N{\rENG}You're magic, Mike. You're fucking magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.68,0:23:22.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,你在吗 迈克\N{\rENG}You there, Mike?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.23,0:23:26.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,己经筹集了二十六万\N{\rENG}Two hundred and sixty-seven thousand
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.35,0:23:28.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,四百三十四…\N{\rENG}four hundred and thirty-four...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.52,0:23:30.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}美元\N{\rENG\i1}dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.40,0:23:32.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,这个数目可不够 威尔斯\N{\rENG}That's not exactly the number I had in mind, Wells.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.98,0:23:35.15,CHS,,0,0,0,,我还可以再借一点\N{\rENG}Well, look, I may be able to borrow a little bit
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.28,0:23:37.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,不过呢\N{\rENG}against it, but, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.20,0:23:38.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,说实话 迈克\N{\rENG}No, you know what? Truth, Mike?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.03,0:23:40.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,目前就这么多钱了\N{\rENG}Th-that's it for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.49,0:23:43.23,CHS,,0,0,0,,就这么多 你能将就吗\N{\rENG}Th-that's it. Can you make it work? Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.96,0:23:46.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,多少我都能将就\N{\rENG}I can make anything work.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.29,0:23:49.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,你们在酒吧工作吗 威尔斯？\N{\rENG}You work out of a bar, Wells?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.34,0:23:52.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,省着点花钱 迈克\N{\rENG}Keeping a lid on expenses, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.67,0:23:54.79,CHS,,0,0,0,,每一分钱都花在刀刃上\N{\rENG}Making the dollar holler.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.93,0:23:58.51,CHS,,0,0,0,,成了\N{\rENG}We're in!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.57,0:24:57.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,点唱机？很有品位\N{\rENG}Record player. That's classy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.11,0:24:59.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,是花的我的钱吗 迈克\N{\rENG}Am I paying for that, Mikey?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.82,0:25:01.53,CHS,,0,0,0,,六名员工\N{\rENG}Six-man crews,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.66,0:25:04.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,每班次十二小时全天开工\N{\rENG}12-hour shifts around the clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.91,0:25:07.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,明天就能出来钻探样品了\N{\rENG}Tomorrow we'll start looking at our core samples.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.70,0:25:09.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,然后我们把成色最好的\N{\rENG}Then we'll send the most promising
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.29,0:25:11.75,CHS,,0,0,0,,送到下游化验室\N{\rENG}down river to the assay lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.88,0:25:13.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,为主矿脉干杯 迈克\N{\rENG}The mother lode, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.05,0:25:17.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,你就在这里 宝贝\N{\rENG}You're out there, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.17,0:26:03.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,发明汉堡包的人很聪明 迈克\N{\rENG}The man that invented the hamburger was smart, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.55,0:26:06.09,CHS,,0,0,0,,而发明芝士汉堡的人\N{\rENG}The man who invented the cheeseburger,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.22,0:26:07.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,更是天\N{\rENG}now, that's the genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.01,0:26:10.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,别问我是哪里来的肉\N{\rENG}Don't ask where the meat came from. Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.89,0:26:14.93,CHS,,0,0,0,,你看过哥伦布的日记吗\N{\rENG}Have you ever read Christopher Columbus' journals?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.06,0:26:16.85,CHS,,0,0,0,,当然没看过\N{\rENG}Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.98,0:26:19.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,在他对西班牙女王的请愿中\N{\rENG}In his petition to the queen of Spain,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.78,0:26:21.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,他承诺\N{\rENG}he promised the conversion
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.65,0:26:26.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,要让大量的人阪依基督教\N{\rENG}to her holy faith of a great number of peoples.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.58,0:26:31.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,他二十六次提到上帝\N{\rENG}And he went on and mentioned God 26 times.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.58,0:26:35.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,而金子\N{\rENG}Gold, on the other hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.17,0:26:39.21,CHS,,0,0,0,,他提到了一百一十四次\N{\rENG}he mentioned 114 times.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.34,0:26:40.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,明白人啊\N{\rENG}Smart dago.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.96,0:26:43.05,CHS,,0,0,0,,有件事我一直想问你 威尔斯\N{\rENG}I've been wanting to ask you something, Wells.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.22,0:26:44.71,CHS,,0,0,0,,你说吧\N{\rENG}Fire away, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.80,0:26:47.13,CHS,,0,0,0,,你手臂上的纹身的是什么意思\N{\rENG}What's the meaning of the tattoo on your arm?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.26,0:26:48.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,哦这是一只乌\N{\rENG}Oh, it's a bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.43,0:26:54.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,出自我小时候看过的一首诗\N{\rENG}It's from a poem I read when I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.31,0:26:56.47,CHS,,0,0,0,,没有脚的乌\N{\rENG}Bird with no feet...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.61,0:26:58.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,在风中睡觉\N{\rENG}sleeps in the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.45,0:27:14.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,化验报告\N{\rENG}Assay!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.29,0:27:16.37,CHS,,0,0,0,,化验报告 化验报告\N{\rENG}Assay! Assay!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.10,0:27:37.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,迈克迈克\N{\rENG}Mike, Mike!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.90,0:27:40.89,CHS,,0,0,0,,这些化验报告一次比一次糟糕\N{\rENG}Hey. These things, they look worse every time we get one.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.02,0:27:42.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,记得我说过要有耐心吗\N{\rENG}Do you remember what I told you about patience?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.78,0:27:44.73,CHS,,0,0,0,,记得 但你记得我说过钱吗\N{\rENG}Yeah, you-you remember what I told you about money?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.74,0:27:45.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 是的  - 咦？\N{\rENG}- Yeah.  - Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.03,0:27:47.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 你说过钱不成问题  - 嗯 这个…\N{\rENG}- You said that it wasn't a problem.  - Well, it...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.86,0:27:49.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,现在成问题了\N{\rENG}it's a fucking problem now!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.37,0:28:38.45,CHS,,0,0,0,,喂\N{\rENG}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.29,0:28:43.68,CHS,,0,0,0,,喂\N{\rENG}Hey! Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.80,0:28:44.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,喂 等等\N{\rENG}Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.80,0:28:45.79,CHS,,0,0,0,,别走 别走\N{\rENG}Stay! Stay! Stay! Stay!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.47,0:28:50.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,喂\N{\rENG}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.51,0:28:51.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,别走\N{\rENG}Stay...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.85,0:28:55.71,CHS,,0,0,0,,喂 别走\N{\rENG}Hey! Stay-
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.85,0:28:57.13,CHS,,0,0,0,,别走\N{\rENG}Stay!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.57,0:29:07.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}除了这些事\N{\rENG\i1}On top of everything else,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.74,0:29:11.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我还染上了严重的疟疾\N{\rENG\i1}I... I got a bad case of malaria,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.11,0:29:13.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}每年有上百万人死于疟疾\N{\rENG\i1}which kills like something like a million people a year,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.70,0:29:15.11,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}听说是这样\N{\rENG\i1}something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.20,0:29:18.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我突然也成了其中一员\N{\rENG\i1}Suddenly, I was on the list.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.34,0:29:29.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,也许我们对工人太苛刻了\N{\rENG}Maybe... maybe we were pushing them too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.92,0:29:32.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,也许我们该宽松点\N{\rENG}Maybe we should just take it easy, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.09,0:29:34.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,让他们入伙\N{\rENG}Cut them in.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.64,0:29:37.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,给他们一些股份\N{\rENG}You know, give them some ownership.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.14,0:29:41.47,CHS,,0,0,0,,也许他们就会回来\N{\rENG}Maybe they'll come back, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.60,0:29:43.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,让他们知道最后能有收获\N{\rENG}Let them know that they got something at the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.77,0:29:45.43,CHS,,0,0,0,,只要找到金矿的话\N{\rENG}you know, when it all works out.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.82,0:29:51.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,给他们一些分成\N{\rENG}Give them a piece of the pie, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.24,0:29:52.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,起来\N{\rENG}Get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.45,0:29:54.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,来起来\N{\rENG}Come on, get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.25,0:30:00.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,我好冷 迈克\N{\rENG}I'm freezing, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.51,0:30:16.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,别让我一无所获的死去\N{\rENG}Don't let me die and have nothing, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.56,0:30:21.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,休息一下吧\N{\rENG}Get some rest now.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.94,0:31:56.61,CHS,,0,0,0,,我要终止勘探\N{\rENG}I'm pulling the plug.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.62,0:32:01.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,不\N{\rENG}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.66,0:32:04.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,不不\N{\rENG}No, no, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.45,0:32:06.29,CHS,,0,0,0,,别终止勘探 迈克\N{\rENG}Don't pull the plug, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.79,0:32:10.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,不 你不能这么做 迈克\N{\rENG}No, no. You can't do that, Mikey.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.21,0:32:13.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们带你离开这里吧威尔斯\N{\rENG}Let's get you out of here, Wells.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.34,0:32:15.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,你有什么办法 迈克\N{\rENG}What's the plan, Mikey?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.26,0:32:17.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,嗯？\N{\rENG}Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.18,0:32:20.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,我知道你肯定有办法 迈克\N{\rENG}Now, I know you got a plan, Mike, hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.89,0:32:23.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,我知道你肯定有办法\N{\rENG}I know you got a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.48,0:32:27.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,是什么办法\N{\rENG}What's the plan, hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.48,0:32:30.47,CHS,,0,0,0,,什么办法\N{\rENG}What's the plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.69,0:32:36.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,他们需要清洁的水\N{\rENG}They need clean water.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.32,0:32:37.73,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果我们能安装过滤系统\N{\rENG}If we get filter systems up here,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.86,0:32:39.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,我想他们可能会回来\N{\rENG}I think they might come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.01,0:32:59.79,CHS,,0,0,0,,我这张维萨卡上还有大约一千八百美元\N{\rENG}I got about $1,800 on this Visa right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.93,0:33:02.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,这个俱乐部餐厅卡上有近五百美元\N{\rENG}Close to 500 on this Diner's Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.31,0:33:11.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,都用上\N{\rENG}Use it all, hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.65,0:33:13.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,都用上迈克\N{\rENG}Use it all, Mikey.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.39,0:33:49.97,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}他去拜访了\N{\rENG\i1}Damned if he didn't go
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.10,0:33:51.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我们每一个工人\N{\rENG\i1}to every single place
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.73,0:33:54.09,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}居住的地方\N{\rENG\i1}that every one of our workers lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.23,0:33:56.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}去过所有无名小溪\N{\rENG\i1}Streams that had no name.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.52,0:33:59.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}所有流向kensana河的溪流\N{\rENG\i1}All feeding the great Kensana River.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.95,0:34:03.15,CHS,,0,0,0,,喂喂\N{\rENG}Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.58,0:34:14.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,知道吗\N{\rENG}But you know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.96,0:34:16.67,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}工人们都回来了\N{\rENG\i1}The workers came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.42,0:34:22.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}接下来几周我依然在受着疟疾的折磨\N{\rENG\i1}I spent the next few weeks in a malarial haze.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.80,0:34:24.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}跟死人一样\N{\rENG\i1}Should've been dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.05,0:34:28.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}一切都是迈克操持的\N{\rENG\i1}But Mike kept it all going.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.35,0:35:09.43,CHS,,0,0,0,,今天几号了\N{\rENG}What day is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.93,0:35:12.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,不知道\N{\rENG}No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.56,0:35:19.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 几月？ - 八月\N{\rENG}- Month?  - August.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.73,0:35:23.47,CHS,,0,0,0,,你一直坐在这儿？\N{\rENG}You been sitting there this whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.65,0:35:25.61,CHS,,0,0,0,,不要高兴太早\N{\rENG}Let's not get carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.78,0:35:32.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,化验报告怎么说什么消息\N{\rENG}What'd the report say? What's the news?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.87,0:35:37.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们又取出了十七个钻探样品\N{\rENG}We pulled 17 more cores.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.71,0:35:41.67,CHS,,0,0,0,,怎么样\N{\rENG}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.75,0:35:44.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 不行？ - 不行\N{\rENG}- No good?  - No good.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.59,0:35:45.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,恩\N{\rENG}Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.93,0:35:49.63,CHS,,0,0,0,,不是一般的行\N{\rENG}More in the vicinity of great.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.31,0:35:54.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,去你的别拿我开心\N{\rENG}Fuck you, Mike. Don't mess with me, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.85,0:35:59.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,每吨含金量八盎司\N{\rENG}Eighth of an ounce per ton.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.95,0:36:13.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,每什么八盎司\N{\rENG}Eighth... eighth of an ounce per what?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.95,0:36:16.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,每吨含金量八盎司\N{\rENG}Eighth of an ounce per ton.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.75,0:36:22.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,你什么意思迈克\N{\rENG}What... what are you... what are you saying, Mike?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.88,0:36:25.25,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们找到了\N{\rENG}We got a strike in.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.59,0:36:27.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们找到了金矿？\N{\rENG}We got a gold mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.51,0:36:31.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 我们找到了金矿？ - 我们找到了金矿\N{\rENG}- We got a gold mine?  - We got a gold mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.68,0:36:39.43,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们找到金矿了迈克我们找到金矿了\N{\rENG}We got a gold mine, Mike! We got a gold mine, Mike!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.56,0:36:41.89,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 我们找到金矿了  - 我们找到金矿了\N{\rENG}- We got a gold mine.  - We got a goddamn gold mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.02,0:36:47.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们找到金矿了\N{\rENG}We got a gold mine! We got a goddamn gold mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.11,0:36:48.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们找到\N{\rENG}We got a goddamn...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.70,0:36:50.11,CHS,,0,0,0,,金矿了\N{\rENG}Gold mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.20,0:36:51.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们找到金矿了\N{\rENG}We got a gold mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.82,0:36:53.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,我就知道 我就知道\N{\rENG}I knew it, I knew it,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.03,0:36:55.65,CHS,,0,0,0,,我就知道 我就知道 我就知道\N{\rENG}I knew it, I knew it, I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.25,0:37:00.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们找到金矿了\N{\rENG}We got a goddamn gold mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.75,0:37:02.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,去死吧 蚊子\N{\rENG}Fuck you, mosquitoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.05,0:37:06.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}那一刻\N{\rENG\i1}That moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.21,0:37:09.55,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我无法描述那种感觉\N{\rENG\i1}there's no way I could possibly describe the feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.68,0:37:11.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}很奇妙一点点砂金\N{\rENG\i1}It's amazing how a little gold dust
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.68,0:37:13.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}就能改变一切\N{\rENG\i1}can just change everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.01,0:37:17.47,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}反正不管是好是坏 征程己经开始\N{\rENG\i1}Now, for better or worse, the ride had begun,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.60,0:37:19.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}多么艰难的征程啊\N{\rENG\i1}and what a goddamn ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.15,0:37:23.23,CHS,,0,0,0,,好吧好吧\N{\rENG}Okay, Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.36,0:37:24.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,感谢上帝\N{\rENG}Oh, thank God.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.44,0:37:28.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 敬给这一行里最棒的团队  - 我靠\N{\rENG}- To the best goddamn team in the business.  - Fucking-A.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.90,0:37:30.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,你是正人君子 肯尼\N{\rENG}You're a stand-up guy, Kenny.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.15,0:37:32.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 肯分享财富  - 疯了 是吗？\N{\rENG}- Sharing the wealth.  - Crazy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.82,0:37:35.61,CHS,,0,0,0,,为主矿脉干杯\N{\rENG}To the mother lode. The mother lode.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.21,0:37:47.79,CHS,,0,0,0,,好 宝贝 帮我个忙\N{\rENG}All right, baby. Do me a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.88,0:37:49.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,闭上眼睛好吗\N{\rENG}Close your eyes, will ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.47,0:37:51.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 好  - 用手蒙着\N{\rENG}- All right.  - Cover them with your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.80,0:37:54.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 别睁开  - 好的\N{\rENG}- Keep 'em closed.  - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.64,0:37:58.97,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 我扶着你 我扶着你  - 好的\N{\rENG}- I got you. I got you. I got you.  - Oh. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.06,0:38:05.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,一二三\N{\rENG}One, two, three.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.03,0:38:12.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,这里将是我们的家\N{\rENG}It's gonna be our place.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.91,0:38:15.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,远离一切 超越一切 就像我们一直所希望的\N{\rENG}Away from it all, above it all, just like we always wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.70,0:38:17.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,你喜欢这里吗\N{\rENG}You like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.16,0:38:18.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 呵呵  - 是的 是的\N{\rENG}- Huh?  - Yes, of... Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.87,0:38:22.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,你看 房子就盖在这里\N{\rENG}Okay, look... the house... right here, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.87,0:38:25.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,厨房面朝那里 客厅在这里\N{\rENG}The kitchen, facing there. The great room over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.67,0:38:27.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 两个壁炉  - 嗯\N{\rENG}- Two fireplaces.  - No...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.63,0:38:28.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们能负担得起吗\N{\rENG}Can we afford this?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.80,0:38:30.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,快了 亲爱的 快了\N{\rENG}Almost, baby. Almost. We're almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.80,0:38:32.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,看这里 这一头是两个卧室\N{\rENG}All right, look at this. Couple bedrooms on that end.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.97,0:38:34.63,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 这一头也有两个卧室  - 不错\N{\rENG}- Couple bedrooms on that end.  - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.76,0:38:36.67,CHS,,0,0,0,,看看这孩子们的游乐场\N{\rENG}Look at this playground for the kids, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.80,0:38:38.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,你想生几个孩子？\N{\rENG}How many kids you want to have?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.98,0:38:45.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}厨房必须在这里\N{\rENG\i1}Kitchen has to stay over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.48,0:38:46.97,CHS,,0,0,0,,要在这里\N{\rENG}We gotta put it over here
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.11,0:38:48.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 有清晨的阳光  - 是的\N{\rENG}- to get the morning light.  - Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.44,0:38:49.93,CHS,,0,0,0,,这一头是第二个厨房\N{\rENG}And a second kitchen over on this side.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.94,0:38:52.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,小溪那边是第三个\N{\rENG}A third one across the creek.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.15,0:38:54.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}靡鹿那边是第四个厨房\N{\rENG\i1}A fourth one up there with the elk.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.42,0:39:14.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 肯尼 肯尼  - 嗯？\N{\rENG}- Kenny, Kenny.  - Mm?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.63,0:39:15.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,这位是沃特・基勒\N{\rENG}This is Walt Kealer.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.09,0:39:17.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 《淘金者》杂志的出版人  - 嗯\N{\rENG}- He publishes <i>Gold Digger{\i0} magazine.  - Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.01,0:39:20.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们的订阅读者达到五十万\N{\rENG}We reach half a million subscribers,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.14,0:39:21.55,CHS,,0,0,0,,他们都想知道\N{\rENG}and they'd all love to know
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.64,0:39:23.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,你在印尼的经历\N{\rENG}what you got cooking over there in Indonesia.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.48,0:39:25.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果你有空 我请你喝一杯\N{\rENG}If you have a minute, I'll buy you a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.31,0:39:29.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,把他让给你了 沃特\N{\rENG}He's all yours, Walt.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.03,0:39:35.31,CHS,,0,0,0,,我也是《淘金者》杂志的读者\N{\rENG}Hell, I read <i>Gold Digger{\i0} magazine.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.45,0:39:37.31,CHS,,0,0,0,,到这里来吧\N{\rENG}Come on over.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.45,0:39:39.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,据说只要拿下这个金矿 你就能获得金镐奖\N{\rENG}They say you bring this in, you'll get the Golden Pickaxe.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.49,0:39:41.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 得了吧  - 你怎么看\N{\rENG}- Aw, shut up.  - What do you say about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.33,0:39:44.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,我看你这话是败我的人品\N{\rENG}I'd say you probably just jinxed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.66,0:39:47.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 你估计有多少盎司金子  - 嗯…\N{\rENG}- How many ounces you guessing?  - Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.79,0:39:50.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,上百万 沃特 绝对有上百万\N{\rENG}Millions, Walt. Absolutely millions.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.75,0:39:51.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,淘金？\N{\rENG}Placer mining?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.09,0:39:54.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,不 是矿石 这是真家伙\N{\rENG}No. Hard rock. This is varsity ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.72,0:39:56.21,CHS,,0,0,0,,基础设施如何\N{\rENG}How's the infrastructure?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.34,0:39:57.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,正从零开始建起\N{\rENG}Building it from the ground up.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.68,0:40:03.05,CHS,,0,0,0,,你想对\N{\rENG}Any message you'd like to give
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.18,0:40:05.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,《淘金者》杂志的读者说些什么\N{\rENG}to the readers of <i>Gold Digger{\i0} magazine?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.90,0:40:14.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,你翻开的最后一张牌才是唯一重要的\N{\rENG}The last card you turn over is the only one that matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.28,0:40:17.11,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 肯尼 很高兴见到你  - 早上好 贝弗利\N{\rENG}- Kenny, it's good to see you.  - Good morning, Beverly.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.20,0:40:19.11,CHS,,0,0,0,,克莱夫一向可好\N{\rENG}Clive, how are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.24,0:40:21.61,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 你来了  - 很高兴见到你先生\N{\rENG}- There he is.  - Good to see you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.74,0:40:23.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 很高兴见到你孩子  - 嗯\N{\rENG}- It's good to see you, son.  - Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.83,0:40:26.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,我和你父亲\N{\rENG}You know, your father and I,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.66,0:40:28.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们一起开始这一行\N{\rENG}we started together in this business.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.92,0:40:31.45,CHS,,0,0,0,,其实是他拉着我一起干的\N{\rENG}Hell, I mean, he put me in the business.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.59,0:40:33.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,这事你知道\N{\rENG}I don't have to tell you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.34,0:40:36.67,CHS,,0,0,0,,他对你一直评价很高 克莱夫\N{\rENG}He always spoke very highly of you, Clive.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.80,0:40:38.63,CHS,,0,0,0,,他是我认识的最好的人之一\N{\rENG}He's one of the best men I ever knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.72,0:40:40.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 是啊  - 现在\N{\rENG}- Yeah.  - Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.10,0:40:43.13,CHS,,0,0,0,,你们的第一批化验结果\N{\rENG}You have gone from four to 23 cents
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.26,0:40:45.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,己经从百分之四提高到百分之二十三\N{\rENG}on your first assay results.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.47,0:40:48.47,CHS,,0,0,0,,然后又挖出两个样品来确认这一发现？\N{\rENG}And you pulled in two more to confirm those findings?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.56,0:40:50.43,CHS,,0,0,0,,是三个\N{\rENG}Three more.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.56,0:40:51.68,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 三个？ - 嗯\N{\rENG}- Three more?  - Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.86,0:40:53.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,这真是太好了\N{\rENG}Well, that's fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.19,0:40:56.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,我想认购\N{\rENG}Well, I would like to underwrite
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.24,0:40:59.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,瓦肖公司的股票\N{\rENG}a private placement of Washoe stock.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.61,0:41:01.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,我相信我们可以筹集\N{\rENG}And I believe that we can raise
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.20,0:41:03.31,CHS,,0,0,0,,八百到一千万美元\N{\rENG}anywhere between $8 million and $10 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.49,0:41:04.73,CHS,,0,0,0,,资金的确是\N{\rENG}Well, capital is definitely
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.87,0:41:06.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,目前很首要的问题\N{\rENG}at the top of our agenda right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.70,0:41:08.07,CHS,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\rENG}Well, yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.21,0:41:10.79,CHS,,0,0,0,,很多人都想做这个交易\N{\rENG}And a lot of people are going to want to make this deal,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.92,0:41:12.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,但历史是在我们一边\N{\rENG}but history is on our side.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.42,0:41:13.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\rENG}Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.79,0:41:15.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,你如果早来找我谈就好了\N{\rENG}But I just wish you'd brought this to me sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.46,0:41:18.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 我从一开始就可以资助你  - 嗯\N{\rENG}- I could have helped you from the get-go.  - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.55,0:41:21.71,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 我们现在见面了  - 是的\N{\rENG}- Well, here we are.  - Here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.84,0:41:23.25,CHS,,0,0,0,,劳埃德\N{\rENG}Lloyd...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.39,0:41:25.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,去给我倒杯咖啡\N{\rENG}top that off for me, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.72,0:41:29.93,CHS,,0,0,0,,黑咖啡 加点调味\N{\rENG}Straight black with a spicer chaser.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.37,0:41:52.33,CHS,,0,0,0,,威尔斯先生 咖啡\N{\rENG}Mr. Wells, uh, coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.46,0:41:53.79,CHS,,0,0,0,,好的 劳埃德 谢谢\N{\rENG}There we are, Lloyd. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.88,0:41:55.99,CHS,,0,0,0,,斯坦顿先生 威尔斯先生同意\N{\rENG}Stanton, Mr. Wells has agreed
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.13,0:41:59.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,卖给我们 但有个条件\N{\rENG}to give us his business on one condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.88,0:42:04.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,劳埃德 我要你\N{\rENG}Lloyd, I want you
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.35,0:42:06.43,CHS,,0,0,0,,亲自负责我的帐户\N{\rENG}to personally handle my account.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.51,0:42:08.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,我要你\N{\rENG}I-I need you to be
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.31,0:42:09.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,二十四小时随叫随到\N{\rENG}available to me 24/7,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.98,0:42:14.31,CHS,,0,0,0,,就像是我的随从一般\N{\rENG}365, as you will be riding shotgun in my jockstrap.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.44,0:42:17.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,没问题 好的 谢谢\N{\rENG}Absolutely. Yes. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.27,0:42:18.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,那我们别站在这儿了\N{\rENG}Well, let's quit standing around here
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.57,0:42:20.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,去赚钱吧\N{\rENG}and go make some goddamn money, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.11,0:42:21.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,我赞同\N{\rENG}That sounds good to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.03,0:42:25.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,肯尼 肯尼\N{\rENG}Kenny? Kenny?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.82,0:42:27.61,CHS,,0,0,0,,肯尼你看了上一份报告吗\N{\rENG}Kenny, did you read the last report?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.87,0:42:31.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}肯尼 你看了上一份报告吗\N{\rENG\i1}Kenny, did you read the last report?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.50,0:42:32.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}是的 是的\N{\rENG\i1}Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.92,0:42:35.75,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我现在正在看 我的天\N{\rENG\i1}No, I'm looking at them right now. Holy shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.88,0:42:38.49,CHS,,0,0,0,,我的天就对了 朋友\N{\rENG}Holy shit is right, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.72,0:42:45.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}真是难以置信\N{\rENG\i1}No, it's unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.60,0:42:47.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,我的天\N{\rENG}Holy shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.06,0:42:49.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}鲍比 我从这里\N{\rENG\i1}Bobby, I can hear your wife
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.06,0:42:51.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,就能听到你老婆笑了\N{\rENG}smiling from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.39,0:42:52.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,回到了你的老地方了 肯尼\N{\rENG}Right back where you belong, Kenny.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.02,0:42:55.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,这办公楼里有很多鬼 诸位\N{\rENG}Yeah, there's a lot of ghosts in this building, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.52,0:42:57.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,干得好 托德\N{\rENG}Oh, nice work, Todd!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.90,0:42:59.81,CHS,,0,0,0,,哇\N{\rENG}Whoo-hoo-hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.55,0:43:24.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\rENG}All right, men.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.97,0:43:27.13,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们的股票将要上涨了\N{\rENG}Now, this stock is going to start cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.26,0:43:28.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,你们一定要卖掉一点\N{\rENG}Make sure you put a little bit away.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.93,0:43:31.51,CHS,,0,0,0,,卖掉一些 为长远考虑\N{\rENG}Sell some. Just the long way. Just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.60,0:43:32.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 尤其是你  - 怎么了\N{\rENG}- Especially you.  - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.02,0:43:34.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 卖掉一些  - 我…\N{\rENG}- Put a little bit away.  - I...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.27,0:43:35.43,CHS,,0,0,0,,你这人从来\N{\rENG}For the first time in your life,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.44,0:43:36.97,CHS,,0,0,0,,不做最坏的打算\N{\rENG}think rainy day, Bobby, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.10,0:43:38.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 好的 好的  - 嗨\N{\rENG}- Of-of course. Of course.  - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.52,0:43:39.93,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 什么？ - 好吗\N{\rENG}- What?  - Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.07,0:43:42.31,CHS,,0,0,0,,好的 好\N{\rENG}Okay. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.50,0:43:56.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们要发大财了\N{\rENG}Oh, we're going to be so fucking rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.47,0:44:13.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,至少装出工作的样子\N{\rENG}At least look like you're working, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.69,0:44:21.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,什么事\N{\rENG}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.03,0:44:27.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,这是什么\N{\rENG}What do you got?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.66,0:44:29.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,投资计划\N{\rENG}Wildcatters, basically.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.57,0:44:31.99,CHS,,0,0,0,,这个叫迈克・阿科斯塔的人取得了一些成功\N{\rENG}This Mike Acosta has had some success. Copper.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.12,0:44:34.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,要被弗里波特接管\N{\rENG}Got taken over by Freeport Mac.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.54,0:44:37.37,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 详细情况都在里面  - 我听说过阿科斯塔\N{\rENG}- It's all in there.  - Yeah. I've heard of Acosta.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.71,0:44:41.95,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 这个计划不错  - 我们先从\N{\rENG}- I like this.  - But I think We start
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.09,0:44:44.37,CHS,,0,0,0,,好消息开始 有百分之五十的股票\N{\rENG}with the good news, which is that we are, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.51,0:44:47.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,已经卖出去 我们想为你们\N{\rENG}50% allocated and, uh, we want to set aside, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.09,0:44:49.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,留出剩下百分之五十的三十\N{\rENG}30 of the remaining 50 for you boys...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.97,0:44:52.25,CHS,,0,0,0,,这里还有吃的 午餐时别喝酒\N{\rENG}There's more food here. Don't drink through lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.39,0:44:53.55,CHS,,0,0,0,,好吗\N{\rENG}All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.64,0:44:55.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,只是吃点东西\N{\rENG}Or just eat something as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.72,0:44:57.43,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 喂 凯  - 电话\N{\rENG}- Hey, Kay!  - Phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.56,0:45:00.68,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 怎么了  - 电话\N{\rENG}- What?  - Phone, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.85,0:45:02.81,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 那一个 谢谢你  - 那部电话要我接吗\N{\rENG}- That one. Thank you.  - You want me to answer it?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.11,0:45:06.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\rENG}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.82,0:45:09.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,瓦肖矿业公司 你要找谁\N{\rENG}Uh, Washoe Mining. How may I direct your call?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.66,0:45:11.99,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 肯尼・威尔斯  - 请稍等\N{\rENG}- Hi. Uh, Kenneth Wells, please.  - Please hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.07,0:45:14.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,肯尼 找你的电话\N{\rENG}Kenny, you got a call!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.83,0:45:18.41,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 谢谢你 亲爱的  - 爱你 宝贝\N{\rENG}- Thank you, dear.  - Love you, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.54,0:45:19.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\rENG}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.54,0:45:20.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,我是肯尼・威尔斯\N{\rENG}Kenny Wells.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.79,0:45:24.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,我是纽约布朗＆托马斯公司的布莱恩・伍尔夫\N{\rENG}This is Brian Woolf at Brown, Thomas in New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.63,0:45:26.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,我是矿业和石油集团的\N{\rENG}I'm with the minerals and oil group.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.76,0:45:28.21,CHS,,0,0,0,,不会吧\N{\rENG}No shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.76,0:45:34.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\rENG}Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.10,0:45:36.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\rENG}Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.02,0:45:39.51,CHS,,0,0,0,,这很好 布莱恩\N{\rENG}Well, that sounds outstanding, Brian.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.64,0:45:41.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,告诉你\N{\rENG}And let me tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.23,0:45:42.81,CHS,,0,0,0,,我很期待\N{\rENG}I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.65,0:45:44.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\rENG}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.66,0:45:55.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,他们要收购我\N{\rENG}They're fucking flying me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.99,0:45:57.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,他们要收购我\N{\rENG}They're fucking flying me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.45,0:45:59.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\rENG}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.92,0:46:04.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}在我看来\N{\rENG\i1}Yeah, the way I see it,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.96,0:46:08.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}银行是干什么的 谁知道呢\N{\rENG\i1}what banks do... who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.67,0:46:11.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}但建成这个国家的不是那些西装革履的人\N{\rENG\i1}But what made this country is not tight asses in suits...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.13,0:46:13.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}无意冒犯 先消消气\N{\rENG\i1}No offense... Taking the easy way down,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.59,0:46:15.63,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}而是我和迈克这样的实干家\N{\rENG\i1}but guys like me and Mike who jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.76,0:46:17.13,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我们现在搞的\N{\rENG\i1}What we have
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.26,0:46:19.51,CHS,,0,0,0,,是非公开配售\N{\rENG}is a private placement in play here.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.64,0:46:22.47,CHS,,0,0,0,,己经有超过百分之五十被订购了\N{\rENG}Already over 50% subscribed.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.60,0:46:24.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果一切顺利的话\N{\rENG}Now, if the numbers keep coming in good,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.81,0:46:27.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,这是肯定的\N{\rENG}which... they're fucking going to,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.61,0:46:30.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,天空是这件事的极限\N{\rENG}the sky is the limit on this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.28,0:46:31.81,CHS,,0,0,0,,你不必向我们推销 我们做过调查\N{\rENG}You don't have to sell us. We've done the math.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.82,0:46:33.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,我相信你们发现的\N{\rENG}We believe you're sitting on
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.11,0:46:34.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,是十年来最大的金矿\N{\rENG}the largest gold find of the decade.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.07,0:46:38.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,我可以坦白说吗 威尔斯先生\N{\rENG}May I speak plainly, Mr. Wells?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.45,0:46:40.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,当然 布莱恩 这是唯一的交谈方式\N{\rENG}Of course, Brian. That's the only way to speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.87,0:46:43.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们的客户希望能看到切实可行的计划\N{\rENG}Our clients are going to want to see a serious plan
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.33,0:46:46.67,CHS,,0,0,0,,能把一个不稳定地区的化验结果\N{\rENG}to turn lab results in a volatile region
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.75,0:46:49.21,CHS,,0,0,0,,变成我们愿意押上自己声誉的投资\N{\rENG}into an investment we can all stake our reputations on.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.34,0:46:50.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,这不成问题\N{\rENG}It's not going to be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.34,0:46:51.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,不这不是问题本身\N{\rENG}No, it's not a problem, per se,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.63,0:46:54.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,但事实是你们两个都没有\N{\rENG}but the fact remains that neither of you have taken
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.26,0:46:55.97,CHS,,0,0,0,,把这么大规模的金矿投入生产\N{\rENG}a find of this magnitude through production.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.05,0:46:58.17,CHS,,0,0,0,,等一下 布莱恩\N{\rENG}Wait just a minute there, Brian.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.31,0:47:00.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们发现了金矿 我们可以开采\N{\rENG}We-we found it, we can dig it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.97,0:47:02.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,没什么复杂的 实际上从历史上看\N{\rENG}It's not that complicated. Actually,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.39,0:47:04.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,这种事有可能极为复杂\N{\rENG}historically, we found it could be quite complicated,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.39,0:47:06.13,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们希望有机会\N{\rENG}and we'd like the opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.23,0:47:09.27,CHS,,0,0,0,,帮你们制定经营计划\N{\rENG}to help you formulate how you present the operation side.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.07,0:47:13.81,CHS,,0,0,0,,你具体是什么意思\N{\rENG}Wh-what-what exactly does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.95,0:47:15.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,我希望两位考虑\N{\rENG}I'd like you both to consider
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.61,0:47:17.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,增加一个战略合作伙伴\N{\rENG}bringing on a strategic partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.20,0:47:19.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,噢\N{\rENG}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.95,0:47:22.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,好\N{\rENG}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.70,0:47:25.41,CHS,,0,0,0,,你们有没有谁\N{\rENG}Have any of you ever
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.54,0:47:27.75,CHS,,0,0,0,,穿着你们手工制造的休闲鞋\N{\rENG}set one of your... your handmade loafers
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.84,0:47:30.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,亲自下过山洞\N{\rENG}down in the hole in the side of a mountain?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.05,0:47:32.75,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 没有  - 但我们有\N{\rENG}- No.  - No. We have.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.88,0:47:34.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,瓦肖公司有这传统\N{\rENG}Washoe has history.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.47,0:47:36.71,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们对瓦肖公司做过相当详尽的分析\N{\rENG}We've done a fairly thorough analysis of Washoe,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.84,0:47:39.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,威尔斯先生我们觉得你们需要战略帮助\N{\rENG}Mr. Wells, and we feel like you need strategic help.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.01,0:47:43.13,CHS,,0,0,0,,不 没门 这是新时代\N{\rENG}No. No way. No. This is a new day, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.27,0:47:45.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,而印尼是完全不同的\N{\rENG}And Indonesia is goddamn different.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.52,0:47:47.73,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们可以帮你把金子运下山\N{\rENG}We can help you get off the side of that mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.90,0:47:48.93,CHS,,0,0,0,,我不需要帮助\N{\rENG}I don't need any help
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.04,0:47:51.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,就能把金子运下山\N{\rENG}getting off the side of the goddamn mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.19,0:47:52.85,CHS,,0,0,0,,这事我能摆平\N{\rENG}I can land this plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.99,0:47:54.07,CHS,,0,0,0,,我能\N{\rENG}I can't
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.32,0:47:57.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,威尔斯来找我\N{\rENG}Wells came and found me.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.91,0:47:59.65,CHS,,0,0,0,,我得承认 我当时正处于低谷\N{\rENG}I was at a low point, I have to admit.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.78,0:48:03.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,在这一行是常事 有起有伏\N{\rENG}It happens in this business, ups and downs.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.54,0:48:06.65,CHS,,0,0,0,,但他资助了我用他的晨后一分钱\N{\rENG}But he backed me with his last cent,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.79,0:48:09.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,不仅如此他还冒着生命危险\N{\rENG}and more than that, he risked his life,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.17,0:48:10.87,CHS,,0,0,0,,差点搭上自己的命\N{\rENG}almost lost it, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.00,0:48:13.75,CHS,,0,0,0,,有一段时间是挺悬的\N{\rENG}It was touch and go there for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.84,0:48:16.67,CHS,,0,0,0,,而现在我们抓住了牛角\N{\rENG}And now we have the bull by its horns.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.76,0:48:18.97,CHS,,0,0,0,,那可是很大的牛角\N{\rENG}And, boys, they're big fucking horns.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.14,0:48:20.55,CHS,,0,0,0,,我跟最优秀的人合作过\N{\rENG}I've worked with the best,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.64,0:48:24.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我可以告诉你们肯尼・威尔斯就是其中一员\N{\rENG}and I can tell you Kenny Wells is up there with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.14,0:48:27.13,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们绝不是\N{\rENG}We're not by any stretch of the imagination
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.27,0:48:29.51,CHS,,0,0,0,,让你们退居二线\N{\rENG}suggesting at this moment that anybody take a backseat.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.65,0:48:31.93,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 只是考虑一下战略伙伴  - 绝不可能\N{\rENG}- Just be open to strategic alliances.  - No fucking...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.04,0:48:33.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,方法！\N{\rENG}way!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.07,0:48:38.81,CHS,,0,0,0,,这是我的钱\N{\rENG}It's a dime out of every one of my dollars,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.82,0:48:39.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,不是你们的钱\N{\rENG}not your dollars!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.82,0:48:41.15,CHS,,0,0,0,,我刚就己经拒绝了\N{\rENG}I said no a second ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.28,0:48:42.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果你们想投资 我们有金矿\N{\rENG}You want to invest? We got the gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.83,0:48:44.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们可以谈\N{\rENG}We can talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.24,0:48:45.95,CHS,,0,0,0,,并不需要什么伙伴\N{\rENG}Don't need a fucking partner. I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.08,0:48:48.45,CHS,,0,0,0,,关于这种事\N{\rENG}You know, there's something about...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.58,0:48:50.95,CHS,,0,0,0,,找到金矿\N{\rENG}finding gold...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.08,0:48:53.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,其困难程度是无法用语言描述的\N{\rENG}that is so difficult to put into words.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.17,0:48:57.75,CHS,,0,0,0,,非常的难\N{\rENG}It's real difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.68,0:49:02.13,CHS,,0,0,0,,要靠舌头来品尝\N{\rENG}Taste of it on your tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.26,0:49:04.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,靠手指来触摸\N{\rENG}The feel of it between your fingers,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.85,0:49:07.09,CHS,,0,0,0,,电击般的感觉\N{\rENG}it's... it's electric.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.14,0:49:11.31,CHS,,0,0,0,,就像是毒品\N{\rENG}It's like a drug,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.44,0:49:13.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,因为能让你上瘾\N{\rENG}'cause it hooks you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.90,0:49:17.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,而这正是你们在城市里体验不到的\N{\rENG}And it's precisely what you're missing here in the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.15,0:49:19.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,所以我们之间才很难交谈\N{\rENG}It's what makes it so hard for us to have this conversation
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.53,0:49:22.11,CHS,,0,0,0,,因为你们从未有过这种感觉\N{\rENG}because you have never felt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.62,0:49:26.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,我给你们个建议\N{\rENG}So I have a proposal for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.91,0:49:28.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,把你们的机构投资者找来\N{\rENG}Put together your institutional players,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.96,0:49:32.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,那些掌管大笔资金的人\N{\rENG}the guys who rep the big money.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.46,0:49:35.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,谁想实地感受一下的话\N{\rENG}Whoever needs to kick the tires on this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.63,0:49:38.79,CHS,,0,0,0,,我会带他们去河上做一次旅行\N{\rENG}I will take them on a little trip up the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.63,0:49:43.63,CHS,,0,0,0,,那么 是阿科斯塔\N{\rENG}So... it was Acosta
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.76,0:49:46.13,CHS,,0,0,0,,提出的去Kensana的公费旅游？\N{\rENG}who proposed the-the junket in Kensana?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.26,0:49:48.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,还是你们一起商量的办法\N{\rENG}Or did you cook that up together?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.98,0:49:51.47,CHS,,0,0,0,,詹宁斯你不明白\N{\rENG}Oh, Jennings, you're... you're not getting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.60,0:49:55.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们不觉得需要商量任何办法\N{\rENG}Look, we-we didn't feel like we had to cook up anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.57,0:49:57.85,CHS,,0,0,0,,四面八方的人都来主动找我\N{\rENG}I mean, I had people coming at me from all sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.99,0:49:59.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,我的邻居哈特・哈伯德\N{\rENG}My-my neighbor, Hart Hubbard,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.90,0:50:01.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,他是草坪护理专业人员\N{\rENG}he's a lawn care professional.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.91,0:50:03.99,CHS,,0,0,0,,平时只担心凯的桑树\N{\rENG}Usually only worried about Kay's mulberry tree
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.12,0:50:05.53,CHS,,0,0,0,,伸到他家的院子里来\N{\rENG}leaning over the back of his fence,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.66,0:50:07.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,但现在 他也用起了采矿术语\N{\rENG}but now he's dropping mining terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.00,0:50:10.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,喂 肯尼 Kensana河的金矿纯度是多少\N{\rENG}"Hey, Kenny, how's the grade purity over there at Kensana?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.91,0:50:13.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,我听说很高 样品频率是多少\N{\rENG}I hear it's great. How about the core frequency?"
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.75,0:50:16.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,这是哈特・哈伯德的话一个以修剪草坪为业的人\N{\rENG}Hart fucking Hubbard. He mows grass for a living.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.34,0:50:18.67,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 我们询问过哈伯德先生  - 总之我的意思是\N{\rENG}- We interviewed Mr. Hubbard.  - What I'm saying is we didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.67,0:50:20.13,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们不需要想什么办法\N{\rENG}think we needed to cook up anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.13,0:50:21.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,谁都想投资\N{\rENG}Everybody wanted in.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.47,0:50:24.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,那么 的确是阿斯科特提出来的银行家旅游？\N{\rENG}So it was Acosta who proposed the banker junket?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.98,0:50:32.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rENG}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.94,0:50:36.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,这招很高明\N{\rENG}It was a genius move.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.86,0:50:39.31,CHS,,0,0,0,,出了机场之后\N{\rENG}Now, you get outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.44,0:50:42.53,CHS,,0,0,0,,你们要跟紧我 看好自己的饯包\N{\rENG}stick close to me and hang on to your wallets.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.95,0:50:48.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,不坐 不坐\N{\rENG}Come on, come on. No, no, no, no, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.95,0:50:50.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,走开走开\N{\rENG}Back, back, back, back, back, back, back, back, back.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.70,0:50:52.41,CHS,,0,0,0,,他来了\N{\rENG}There he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.54,0:50:55.75,CHS,,0,0,0,,诸位这是迈克・阿科斯塔\N{\rENG}Gentlemen, Mike Acosta.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.88,0:50:57.37,CHS,,0,0,0,,格伦\N{\rENG}Glen.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.50,0:50:58.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿科斯塔\N{\rENG}Acosta.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.92,0:50:59.91,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 鲍勃  - 阿科斯塔\N{\rENG}- Bobby.  - Acosta.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.05,0:51:01.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,杰夫・杰克逊\N{\rENG}Jeff Jackson.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.51,0:51:03.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果谁想反悔的话\N{\rENG}If any one of you wants to turn back,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.72,0:51:05.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,现在还来得及\N{\rENG}this is your chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.22,0:51:07.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\rENG}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.43,0:51:11.51,CHS,,0,0,0,,他吓唬你们呢 欢迎来到印尼\N{\rENG}He's just messing with you. Welcome to Indo, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.77,0:51:14.01,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我们发现金矿后\N{\rENG\i1}When we got the hit,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.14,0:51:16.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,以此为中心在四周勘探\N{\rENG}we stepped out in a radiating pattern
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.27,0:51:19.23,CHS,,0,0,0,,直到我们确定金矿的范围\N{\rENG}and we kept going until we had the definitive picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.36,0:51:21.89,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们在描绘地下地质学\N{\rENG}We're mapping the underlying geology.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.03,0:51:25.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,样品被切成块 然后粉碎\N{\rENG}The cores are cut into sections, and then crushed.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.99,0:51:29.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,然后包装 密封\N{\rENG}They are then bagged and sealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.83,0:51:33.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,这笼子全天有人看守\N{\rENG}This cage is guarded 24/7.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.83,0:51:36.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,保安把样品护送到下游\N{\rENG}Under guard, the samples are sent down river
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.96,0:51:39.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,加里曼丹的独立化验室\N{\rENG}to independent labs in Kalimantan.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.46,0:51:41.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果密封受到任何破坏\N{\rENG}If a seal is broken or damaged in any way,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.67,0:51:44.75,CHS,,0,0,0,,根据法律 化验室就必须舍弃整个样品\N{\rENG}the lab, by law, has to discard the entire sample.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.88,0:51:46.71,CHS,,0,0,0,,所有安保措施都己经到位\N{\rENG}Every safeguard has been put in place
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.84,0:51:48.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,来确保整个过程的安全\N{\rENG}to assure the security of the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.93,0:51:52.67,CHS,,0,0,0,,金刚石锯条 碎石机\N{\rENG}Diamond-tipped saw blades, rock crushers.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.81,0:51:55.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,从大地深处取出的样品\N{\rENG}Core samples being ripped from the guts of the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.39,0:51:57.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,这一切听起来都不错 不过\N{\rENG}It all sounds great, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.44,0:52:01.68,CHS,,0,0,0,,你们还是想看看金子\N{\rENG}you boys want to see some gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.03,0:52:09.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,我竟然在干这种事\N{\rENG}No one's going to believe this shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.70,0:52:11.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,你怎么看\N{\rENG}So, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.20,0:52:14.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,不确定 你呢\N{\rENG}Not sure. What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.08,0:52:16.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿斯科特感觉是个懂行的人\N{\rENG}Acosta seems to know what he's talking about,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.75,0:52:18.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,但另一位就难说了\N{\rENG}but, uh, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.42,0:52:22.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,喂喂\N{\rENG}Hey. Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.92,0:52:24.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,过来 过来\N{\rENG}Come here, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.26,0:52:25.75,CHS,,0,0,0,,我好像有所发现\N{\rENG}I think I... I think I got something.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.31,0:52:41.43,CHS,,0,0,0,,看这个\N{\rENG}See this?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.48,0:52:43.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,多一些这种东西\N{\rENG}Few more like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.82,0:52:46.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,就足以铺设华尔街的道路\N{\rENG}you can pave Wall Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.95,0:52:51.61,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}当杰克逊淘出那个金块的时候\N{\rENG\i1}When Jackson pulled that nugget out,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.62,0:52:52.95,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}他们都信服了\N{\rENG\i1}we had 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.03,0:52:54.99,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}布朗＆托马斯公司自豪的宣布\N{\rENG\i1}Brown, Thomas is proud
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.12,0:52:58.45,CHS,,0,0,0,,公开发售两千七百万股\N{\rENG}to announce the public offering of 27 million shares
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.58,0:53:00.79,CHS,,0,0,0,,A级普通股\N{\rENG}of class A common stock
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.92,0:53:03.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,和瓦肖矿业原始股\N{\rENG}and the initial listing of Washoe Mining
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.80,0:53:05.91,CHS,,0,0,0,,在纽约证券交易所\N{\rENG}on the New York Stock Exchange!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.09,0:53:12.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们会赚上一大笔钱\N{\rENG}We're all going to make a lot of fucking money!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.89,0:53:19.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,欢迎下榻华尔道夫酒店 夫人\N{\rENG}Welcome to the Waldorf Astoria, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.56,0:53:23.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们会把您的行李送上楼\N{\rENG}We'll get your bags right upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.13,0:53:45.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,肯尼\N{\rENG}Kenny?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.09,0:53:47.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,你在吗\N{\rENG}Are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.01,0:53:52.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,宝贝\N{\rENG}Baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.51,0:53:54.25,CHS,,0,0,0,,你在哪？\N{\rENG}Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.60,0:53:59.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,啊\N{\rENG}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.94,0:54:01.97,CHS,,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\rENG}Oh, my goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.10,0:54:03.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,你意外吗\N{\rENG}You surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.31,0:54:04.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\rENG}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.52,0:54:08.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,这是你最喜欢的花吧\N{\rENG}It's your favorite flower, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.90,0:54:11.89,CHS,,0,0,0,,亲爱的\N{\rENG}Babe.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.28,0:54:15.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,你真美 凯\N{\rENG}You look beautiful, Kay.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.83,0:54:17.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,过来\N{\rENG}Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.87,0:54:20.53,CHS,,0,0,0,,我想死你了\N{\rENG}I have missed you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.66,0:54:23.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,别提有多想了\N{\rENG}You have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.01,0:54:32.17,CHS,,0,0,0,,这是不是你睡过的最软的床单\N{\rENG}Are these the softest sheets you've ever felt?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.30,0:54:34.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 我觉得是  - 是的\N{\rENG}- Yeah, you know, I think they are.  - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.47,0:54:37.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 想不想滚床单  - 好\N{\rENG}- You want to get under 'em?  - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.11,0:54:54.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,你们好\N{\rENG}Oh, hello, men.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.74,0:54:55.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,诸位 这是凯\N{\rENG}Everyone, meet the lovely Kay.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.99,0:54:57.23,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 布莱恩  - 幸会\N{\rENG}- Brian. Hi.  - Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.24,0:54:58.61,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 霍利斯  - 嗨\N{\rENG}- Hollis. Kay.  - Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.74,0:54:59.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,幸会\N{\rENG}Pleasure. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.00,0:55:01.33,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 这位斯坦帧你认识  - 哎\N{\rENG}- Stanton, you know.  - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.50,0:55:04.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,这一行唯一和我流汗一样多的人\N{\rENG}The only man in this business that sweats as much as I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.37,0:55:06.33,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们来吧\N{\rENG}All right, let's do this, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.46,0:55:08.17,CHS,,0,0,0,,这就是他\N{\rENG}Ah, there he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.34,0:55:09.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,迈克・阿科斯塔独一无二的迈克\N{\rENG}Mike Acosta, the one and only.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.01,0:55:12.21,CHS,,0,0,0,,迈克 这位是凯\N{\rENG}Mike, meet Kay.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.34,0:55:14.63,CHS,,0,0,0,,两个我在世上最喜欢的人\N{\rENG}Two of my favorite people in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.76,0:55:17.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,他为了去见你 还偷了我的表\N{\rENG}You know this one stole my watch to go meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.51,0:55:18.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 你偷了她的手表？ - 噢 不不\N{\rENG}- You stole her watch?  - Oh, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.81,0:55:20.05,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 不 我开玩笑的  - 她只是在开玩笑\N{\rENG}- No... I'm just teasing.  - She's just teasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.06,0:55:21.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 你没开玩笑  - 不，她不是\N{\rENG}- No, you're not.  - No, she's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.31,0:55:22.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,对 没开玩笑\N{\rENG}No, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.56,0:55:24.55,CHS,,0,0,0,,因为不知道时间 我先闪人了\N{\rENG}I didn't know what time it... I got to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.69,0:55:26.85,CHS,,0,0,0,,见到你太好了 迈克\N{\rENG}It's so good to meet you, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.98,0:55:29.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 你肯定很自豪  - 那当然\N{\rENG}- You must be very proud.  - Never doubted for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.07,0:55:35.23,CHS,,0,0,0,,开始吧 五\N{\rENG}Here we go! Five!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.36,0:55:37.27,CHS,,0,0,0,,四 三\N{\rENG}Four! Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.41,0:55:39.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,二 一\N{\rENG}Two! One!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.91,0:55:43.99,CHS,,0,0,0,,耶\N{\rENG}Yeah... baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.12,0:55:46.11,CHS,,0,0,0,,我来为股市开盘了\N{\rENG}I'm ringing the bell, baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.89,0:56:00.67,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}在这个我们一直密切追踪报道的事件中\N{\rENG\i1}In the story we've been following very closely,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.81,0:56:01.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}瓦肖矿业\N{\rENG\i1}Washoe Mining
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.06,0:56:03.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,可能是本年度最佳股票\N{\rENG}may be the stock of the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.73,0:56:04.93,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}在纽约证券交易所\N{\rENG\i1}On their first day
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.06,0:56:07.93,CHS,,0,0,0,,第一天上市瓦肖矿业\N{\rENG}on the New York Stock Exchange, Washoe Mining
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.06,0:56:10.81,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}股价如火箭般蹿升\N{\rENG\i1}turned into a rocket ship today.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.11,0:56:18.95,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 你好 很高兴见到你  - 肯尼 迈克 来吧\N{\rENG}- Hi. Great to meet you.  - Kenny. Mike. Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.75,0:56:25.49,CHS,,0,0,0,,哦\N{\rENG}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.62,0:56:26.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,不用了 谢谢\N{\rENG}No, I'm okay. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.00,0:56:29.33,CHS,,0,0,0,,这和钱都是祖传的基因\N{\rENG}This and the money are in the genes.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.05,0:56:40.71,CHS,,0,0,0,,你好我是肯尼・威尔斯幸会\N{\rENG}How are you? Kenny Wells. Good to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.94,0:56:56.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,这是真事\N{\rENG}True fucking story.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.41,0:57:00.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,在座的谁想知道\N{\rENG}Who at this table wants to know the secret
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.57,0:57:02.31,CHS,,0,0,0,,赌球赢钱的秘诀是什么\N{\rENG}to winning bets at pro football?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.49,0:57:04.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 什么秘诀  - 每次都押东海岸球队\N{\rENG}- What's that?  - Take the east coast team
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.24,0:57:05.68,CHS,,0,0,0,,知道为什么吗\N{\rENG}every fucking time. You know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.83,0:57:09.41,CHS,,0,0,0,,因为西海岸球队在午夜之后才开球\N{\rENG}The west coast team... to them, they're playing after midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.10,0:57:30.93,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 我是瑞秋・希尔  - 嗯\N{\rENG}- Rachel Hill.  - Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.06,0:57:32.68,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 巨人队的球迷  - 肯尼・威尔斯 瑞秋\N{\rENG}- Giants fan.  - Kenny Wells, Rachel.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.86,0:57:34.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,你做什么职业？瑞秋・希尔\N{\rENG}So, what do you do, Rachel Hill?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.19,0:57:35.81,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 投资者公关  - 嗯\N{\rENG}- Investor relations.  - Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.94,0:57:37.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,布朗＆托马斯公司团队的\N{\rENG}Brown, Thomas. On the team.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.65,0:57:39.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,不错 你肯定是\N{\rENG}Cheers to that. You got to be the best-looking one
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.07,0:57:41.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,团队中最漂亮的一个\N{\rENG}on the team, I'll tell you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.49,0:57:45.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,就像一只醉酒的浣熊\N{\rENG}It's like a drunk raccoon
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.79,0:57:47.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,手上拿着蓝宝石\N{\rENG}got a hold of the Hope diamond.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.45,0:57:49.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,不能离它太近了\N{\rENG}You don't want to get too close,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.16,0:57:51.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,但也不能让浣熊跑了\N{\rENG}but you're not going to let it get away either.
