Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.20,1:23:28.91,CHS,,0,0,0,,将把金镐奖授予你\N{\rENG}is gonna honor you with the Golden Pickaxe.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.00,1:23:34.61,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 你是开玩笑吗  - 不是\N{\rENG}- You shittin' me?  - No, I'm not.
