Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.40,1:25:24.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,呃\N{\rENG}uh...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.11,1:25:27.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,穿过来再绕一圈\N{\rENG}and across and around...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.58,1:25:42.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,我很紧张\N{\rENG}I'm nervous.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.75,1:25:45.71,CHS,,0,0,0,,你没问题的\N{\rENG}You're gonna be okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.53,1:26:10.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们每一个\N{\rENG}"Every last one of us
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.78,1:26:14.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,生活在内华达州的人\N{\rENG}"who calls the great state of Nevada home...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.58,1:26:16.91,CHS,,0,0,0,,当初都是带着梦想\N{\rENG}"arrived here...
