Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.43,1:26:33.21,CHS,,0,0,0,,说\N{\rENG}"and said...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:35.56,1:26:37.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,就是这里了\N{\rENG}'This is the place."'
