Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.11,1:26:47.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,还不错\N{\rENG}That's good.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:49.86,1:26:52.15,CHS,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rENG}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:52.28,1:26:54.61,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我们的肯尼・威尔斯\N{\rENG\i1}Our own Kenny Wells!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.20,1:26:57.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,上台来吧丹尼\N{\rENG}Get up here, Kenny!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.14,1:27:24.43,CHS,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rENG}Thank you. Um...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.73,1:27:31.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,我曾祖父\N{\rENG}My great granddad...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.74,1:27:33.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,也是个探矿者\N{\rENG}was one of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.70,1:27:36.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,他乘着马车来到这里 带着一匹马和两头骡子\N{\rENG}He came out here in a wagon with two horses and a mule,
