Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.12,1:27:42.53,CHS,,0,0,0,,到这里慢了下来\N{\rENG}before he slowed down, and it was it was when he got here
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.64,1:27:46.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,最后拉着缰绳说\N{\rENG}that he finally pulled those reins back and said...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.92,1:27:50.25,CHS,,0,0,0,,就是这里了\N{\rENG}"This is the place."
Dialogue: 0,1:27:55.26,1:27:57.09,CHS,,0,0,0,,什么是探矿者\N{\rENG}What is a prospector?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.51,1:28:00.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,别 别\N{\rENG}No, no, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.85,1:28:02.43,CHS,,0,0,0,,我是认真的\N{\rENG}Seriously, what...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.10,1:28:06.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,什么是探矿者\N{\rENG}What is a prospector?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.32,1:28:12.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,就是一个相信\N{\rENG}It's someone who believes...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.74,1:28:16.15,CHS,,0,0,0,,金矿存在的人\N{\rENG}it's out there.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.28,1:28:18.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}他每天早晨醒来\N{\rENG\i1}Who wakes up every morning,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.66,1:28:21.53,CHS,,0,0,0,,一次又一次一次又一次\N{\rENG}again and again, again and again...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.04,1:28:26.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,都相信金矿的存在\N{\rENG}believing it's out there.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.79,1:28:30.45,CHS,,0,0,0,,但其实不存在\N{\rENG}And then it's not.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.59,1:28:33.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 对吗 并没有  - 嗯嗯\N{\rENG}- Right? It's not.  - Mm-hmm. Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.80,1:28:37.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,他站在荒漠的边绿\N{\rENG}And he's standing on the edge of the desert,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.51,1:28:39.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,凝视着\N{\rENG}staring a...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:39.14,1:28:42.35,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}新的一天的日出\N{\rENG\i1}new day's sunrise right in the eye, and...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.43,1:28:44.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}然后听到内心深处\N{\rENG\i1}and he hears that little voice,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.98,1:28:47.31,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}有个声音说：\N{\rENG\i1}a little voice that says...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:49.44,1:28:51.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,前进\N{\rENG}"Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.73,1:28:53.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,继续走\N{\rENG}Keep walking."
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.19,1:28:56.73,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}日头越升越高\N{\rENG\i1}And the sun gets higher and higher,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.86,1:28:58.85,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}照在他身上 他很热\N{\rENG\i1}and it's shining down on him, and he's really hot,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.99,1:29:00.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}而且他没有…\N{\rENG\i1}and he doesn't have
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.03,1:29:01.27,CHS,,0,0,0,,任何可喝的水\N{\rENG}any water to drink,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:01.40,1:29:03.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,和他一起来的人都想回去\N{\rENG}and everybody that came with him wants to turn back,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.00,1:29:05.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,最后也都回去了\N{\rENG}and eventually, they do turn back,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:05.83,1:29:07.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,留下了他\N{\rENG}and there he is.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.83,1:29:09.99,CHS,,0,0,0,,留下他一个人\N{\rENG}And he's all alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.47,1:29:22.63,CHS,,0,0,0,,抱着一个信念\N{\rENG}With the belief...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.69,1:29:30.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,金矿是存在的\N{\rENG}that it's out there, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.27,1:29:32.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,是存在的\N{\rENG}It's out there.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.40,1:29:40.27,CHS,,0,0,0,,这就是探矿者\N{\rENG}That's a prospector.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.16,1:29:44.99,CHS,,0,0,0,,这就是探矿者\N{\rENG}That's a prospector.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.75,1:29:58.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,演讲的太好了 孩子 太好了\N{\rENG}Really great speech, son. Just great. Great.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.86,1:30:16.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 敬给你父亲  - 敬给威尔斯先生\N{\rENG}- To your daddy.  - To Mr. Wells!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:46.08,1:30:47.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\rENG}Mm.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.60,1:30:52.89,CHS,,0,0,0,,喂\N{\rENG}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:56.02,1:30:58.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,什么？\N{\rENG}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:58.82,1:31:00.15,CHS,,0,0,0,,你再说一遍\N{\rENG}Say-say again?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.24,1:31:01.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,我不明白\N{\rENG}No, I-I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:01.90,1:31:03.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\rENG}Wait-wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.88,1:31:23.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,肯尼 这是怎么回事\N{\rENG}Kenny, what's going on? Kenny... what happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.89,1:31:24.97,CHS,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\rENG}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:25.14,1:31:27.17,CHS,,0,0,0,,我会查清楚\N{\rENG}I'm going to find out.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.18,1:31:31.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,我也是一无所知\N{\rENG}I don't know any more than...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:36.56,1:31:39.23,CHS,,0,0,0,,你不会逃脱的\N{\rENG}You're not gonna get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:40.57,1:31:42.15,CHS,,0,0,0,,走开\N{\rENG}Back the fuck off!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.28,1:31:45.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,肯尼一定要把这事解决啊\N{\rENG}Kenny, please fix this!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.91,1:31:48.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,怎么回事 怎么回事\N{\rENG}What happened, huh? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.53,1:31:50.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,独立化验机构\N{\rENG}The independent assayer.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.12,1:31:52.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,他们无法复制迈克的发现\N{\rENG}They couldn't reproduce Mike's findings.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:54.50,1:31:56.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,那里没有金子\N{\rENG}There's no gold.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:56.67,1:31:59.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,那里没有金子一直都没有\N{\rENG}Kenny, there's no goddamn gold. There never was.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.42,1:32:04.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,这不可能\N{\rENG}That's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.14,1:32:07.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,左边的是在瓦肖的样品中\N{\rENG}The image on the left is the type of gold
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.85,1:32:10.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,发现的金子 这是河金\N{\rENG}found in the Washoe samples. This is river gold.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.72,1:32:12.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}注意边绿是圆的\N{\rENG\i1}Notice how the edges are rounded,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.52,1:32:14.97,CHS,,0,0,0,,被河水侵蚀的光滑\N{\rENG}worn smooth by the erosion of water.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.10,1:32:17.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,本该发现的是片金\N{\rENG}What we should have found is flake gold,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.27,1:32:18.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,就是右边的样品\N{\rENG}the sample on the right,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.90,1:32:22.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}直接从岩石提取 边绿粗糙有棱角\N{\rENG\i1}pulled directly from the rock, rough-edged and angular.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:22.99,1:32:25.15,CHS,,0,0,0,,这是被忽略的一个很大的细节\N{\rENG}That's a pretty darn big detail to overlook,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.28,1:32:26.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,不是吗\N{\rENG}wouldn't you say?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.99,1:32:29.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,的确是个很大的细节 但你要知道\N{\rENG}It's a big detail, but... you have to understand,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.95,1:32:32.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,瓦肖样品的其它方面都没有问题\N{\rENG}everything else about the Washoe samples was right.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:33.04,1:32:35.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,可金子是错的\N{\rENG}But the gold was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.25,1:32:38.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,这叫撒盐 意思就是\N{\rENG}It's called salting... It literally means when someone
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.33,1:32:40.95,CHS,,0,0,0,,把金粉撒入岩石样品中\N{\rENG}sprinkles gold dust into a rock sample,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.09,1:32:43.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,就像在牛排上撒盐那样\N{\rENG}like you... salt your steak.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.97,1:32:46.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}这是很古老的技俩\N{\rENG\i1}It is the oldest trick in the book.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:47.01,1:32:48.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}很古老的技俩？\N{\rENG\i1}Oldest trick in the book?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:48.84,1:32:50.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,然而大矿业公司\N{\rENG}And yet major mining corporations,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:50.97,1:32:52.63,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}投资银行审计师\N{\rENG\i1}investment banks, the auditors,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.72,1:32:54.09,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}每个人都被骗了\N{\rENG\i1}everyone was fooled.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:54.23,1:32:56.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们不是被骗\N{\rENG}We weren't fooled.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:56.52,1:32:58.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,只是没去看\N{\rENG}We just didn't look.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.52,1:33:00.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}从所有的外表看\N{\rENG\i1}By all appearances,
