Dialogue: 0,1:33:08.16,1:33:10.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,整个保安系统都形同虚设\N{\rENG}the whole system goes down.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.37,1:33:18.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,对 他说过\N{\rENG}Right. Did he say...
